%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106627781.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJo%20Koy%20received%20backlash%20from%20netizens%20at%20the%2081st%20Golden%20Globes%20for%20his%20'big%20boobie'%20joke%20on%20Barbie%20and%20trolling%20Taylor%20Swift%20over%20her%20relationship%20with%20Travis%20Kelce.%20The%20event%20aimed%20to%20reclaim%20its%20status%20as%20the%20third%20most%20significant%20awards%20show%20of%20the%20year%2C%20but%20Koy's%20jokes%20fell%20flat%20and%20irked%20viewers.%20Koy's%20remark%20about%20Barbie%20being%20a%20plastic%20doll%20with%20big%20boobs%20earned%20him%20awkward%20reactions%20from%20the%20Barbie%20cast%20and%20Taylor%20Swift.%20Fans%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20slam%20the%20host%20for%20his%20distasteful%20remarks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fgolden-globes-2024-jo-koy-slammed-for-his-joke-on-barbie-and-taylor-swift-netizens-say-someone-call-will-smith%2Farticleshow%2F106627781.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20A%20Retired%20US%20Couple%20Used%20A%20Lottery%20Loophole%20To%20Win%20Over%20Rs%20200%20Crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20retired%20couple%20from%20the%20United%20States%20has%20managed%20to%20accumulate%20over%20%2426%20million%20(approximately%20Rs%20200%20crore)%20in%20lottery%20prizes%2C%20thanks%20to%20their%20impressive%20math%20skills.%20Jerry%20and%20Marge%20Selbee%2C%2080%20and%2081%20respectively%2C%20ran%20a%20convenience%20store%20in%20Evart%20until%20they%20sold%20it%20and%20retired%20in%20their%2060s%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2022%2F06%2F16%2Fjerry-and-marge-go-large-retirees-made-millions-gamin-lottery%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20Mr.%20Selbee%C2%A0saw%20a%20brochure%20for%20a%20new%20lottery%20game%20called%20Winfall%20and%20quickly%20figured%20out%20a%20mathematical%20loophole%C2%A0that%20could%20almost%20guarantee%20winning.%C2%A0The%20game%2C%20called%20WinFall%2C%20had%20a%20unique%20feature%20that%20if%20the%20jackpot%20reached%20US%245%20million%20(%247%20million)%20and%20failed%20to%20go%20off%2C%20the%20money%20would%20roll%20down%20to%20ticket%20holders%20with%20fewer%20winning%20numbers.%20He%20was%20sure%20that%20the%20mathematical%20flaw%20would%20mean%20guaranteed%20winnings%20if%20he%20bought%20enough%20tickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Selbee%2C%20who%20majored%20in%20math%20in%20college%2C%20calculated%20that%20if%20he%20spent%20%241%2C100%20on%201%2C100%20tickets%2C%20odds%20are%20he'd%20have%20one%20four-number%20winner%20that%20would%20pay%20out%20%241%2C000%2C%20and%20at%20least%2018%20or%2019%20three-number%20winners%20that%20paid%20%24900.%20That%20meant%20his%20%241%2C100%20investment%20would%20yield%20a%20%241%2C900%20return%2C%20for%20a%20tidy%20profit%20of%20%24800.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20looked%20at%20the%20odds%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20what%20the%20payoff%20would%20be%20and%20I%20did%20a%20risk-reward%20analysis.%20It%20took%20me%20less%20than%20two%20minutes%20to%20figure%20out%20that%20that%20game%20could%20be%20profitable%2C''%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20initially%20experimented%20by%20investing%20%243%2C600%20in%20Winfall%20tickets%2C%20earning%20approximately%20%246%2C300%20in%20winnings.%20After%20that%2C%20he%20bet%20%248%2C000%20and%20again%20doubled%20his%20money%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fjerry-and-marge-selbee-how-a-retired-couple-won-millions-using-a-lottery-loophole-60-minutes-2019-06-09%2F%5C%22%3E%20CBS%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20''If%20I%20played%20%241100%2C%20mathematically%20I'd%20have%20one%20four-number%20winner%20%E2%80%93%20that's%201000%20bucks.%20I%20divided%201100%20by%20six%20instead%20of%2057%2C%20because%20I%20did%20a%20mental%20quick%20dirty%2C%20and%20I%20came%20up%20with%2018.%20So%20I%20knew%20I'd%20have%20either%2018%20or%2019%20three-number%20winners%2C%20and%20that's%2050%20bucks%20each.%20At%2018%2C%20I%20got%20%241000%20for%20a%20four-number%20winner%2C%20and%20I%20got%2018%20three-number%20winners%20worth%20%2450%20each%2C%20so%20that's%20900%20bucks.%20So%20I%20got%20%241100%20invested%20and%20I've%20got%20a%20%241900%20return.%20It's%20just%20basic%20arithmetic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20they%20got%20so%20good%20at%20the%20game%20that%20they%20set%20up%20a%20corporation%2C%20G.S.%20Investment%20Strategies%2C%20and%20invited%20their%20friends%20and%20family%20to%20buy%20into%20the%20business%20for%20%24500%20apiece.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20they%20came%20to%20know%20about%20a%20similar%20Winfall%20lottery%20in%20Massachusetts%2C%20nearly%20700%20miles%20away.%20So%20the%20Selbees%20traveled%20to%20Massachusetts%20every%20time%20there%20was%20a%20rolldown%2C%C2%A0buying%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20tickets%20at%20two%20convenience%20stores.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Selbees%20said%20that%20over%20the%20nine%20years%20they%20played%20Winfall%2C%20their%20group%20won%20a%20total%20of%20%2426%20million%20and%20they%20made%20about%20%248%20million%20in%20profit%20before%20taxes.%C2%A0The%20money%20was%20used%20to%20renovate%20their%20house%20and%20help%20pay%20for%20the%20schooling%20of%20their%20six%20children%2C%2014%20grandchildren%2C%20and%2010%20great-grandchildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20winnings%20and%20large%20purchase%20of%20tickets%20also%20triggered%20an%20investigation%20by%20the%20Inspector%20General.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20discovered%20that%20the%20Selbees%20had%20been%20playing%20by%20the%20rules%20and%20there%20was%20nothing%20illegal%20about%20their%20methods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Selbees'%20story%20now%20has%20become%20the%20inspiration%20for%20the%20new%20movie%20''Jerry%20%26amp%3B%20Marge%20Go%20Large.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704698160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-04%2Fla8o2f1_lottery-650_625x300_25_April_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-a-retired-us-couple-used-a-lottery-loophole-and-math-skills-to-win-over-rs-200-crore-4821462%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202003%2C%20Mr.%20Selbee%20saw%20a%20brochure%20for%20a%20new%20lottery%20game%20called%20Winfall%20and%20quickly%20figured%20out%20a%20mathematical%20loophole.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-a-retired-us-couple-used-a-lottery-loophole-and-math-skills-to-win-over-rs-200-crore-4821462%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-a-retired-us-couple-used-a-lottery-loophole-and-math-skills-to-win-over-rs-200-crore-4821462%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-a-retired-us-couple-used-a-lottery-loophole-and-math-skills-to-win-over-rs-200-crore-4821462%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Handmaid's%20Tale%20Season%206%20all%20deets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704697993000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106629827%2Cimgsize-22654.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fenglish%2Funlocking-the-future-the-handmaids-tale-season-6-release-date-cast-story-and-all-the-details-we-have-so-far%2Farticleshow%2F106629898.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106629898.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESeason%205%20concluded%20with%20June