ot-locals-sources-4635147%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E13%20Killed%20In%20Manipur%20Gunfight%20Near%20Myanmar%20Border%20Not%20Locals%3A%20Sources%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20centre%20at%20that%20time%20left%20us%20alone.%20There%20is%20(still)%20no%20security%20at%20the%20border.%20There%20is%20Assam%20Rifles...%20but%20they%20can't%20handle%20both%20counter-insurgency%20and%20guard%20the%20border.%20And%20now%20we%20have%20(militants)%20camped%20inside%20our%20borders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%20too%20Mr%20Singh%20had%20highlighted%20the%20need%20to%20cancel%2C%20or%20at%20least%20modify%2C%20the%20Free%20Movement%20Regime%2C%20or%20FMR%2C%20and%20to%20fence%20the%201%2C643-km%20Myanmar%20border.%C2%A0He%20said%20there%20were%20instances%20of%20people%20from%20Myanmar%20trying%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20FMR%20to%20enter%20his%20state.%20Many%20were%20forced%20to%20return%20by%20security%20personnel%2C%20but%20there%20may%20be%20others%20who%20slipped%20through%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20porous%20border%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fend-free-movement-regime-in-india-myanmar-border-manipur-chief-minister-n-biren-singh-4417292%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEnd%20'Free%20Movement%20Regime'%20In%20India-Myanmar%20Border%3A%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20thinks%20about%20the%20indigenous%20people%20of%20Manipur.%20Only%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20came%20to%20power%20was%20attention%20paid%20to%20the%20northeast...%20earlier%20governments%2C%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20mention%20names%2C%20they%20left%20us%20alone.%20So%20what%20is%20happening%20now%20is%20because%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20border%20fencing%20is%20a%20must%20and%20free%20movement%20must%20be%20cancelled%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20told%20NDTV.%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20of%20course%2C%20please%20come%20and%20visit...%20but%20there%20is%20an%20international%20norm%20for%20visiting%20foreign%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ExMr%20Singh's%20calls%20have%20been%20backed%20by%20Union%20Minister%20Rajkumar%20Ranjan%20Singh%2C%20who%20this%20week%20told%20NDTV%20%26quot%3Bthe%20situation%20today%20is%20such%20that%20fencing%20is%20a%20must%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsituation-today-is-such-what-union-minister-rajkumar-ranjan-singh-said-on-need-for-india-myanmar-border-fencing-4817446%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BSituation%20Today%20Is%20Such...%26quot%3B%3A%20Union%20Minister%20Calls%20For%20India-Myanmar%20Border%20Fencing%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FMR%20-%20implemented%20in%202018%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government's%20'Act%20East'%20policy%20-%20allows%20hill%20tribe%20members%20from%20either%20India%20or%20Myanmar%20to%20cross%20the%20border%20with%20a%20specific%20pass%20(valid%20for%20one%20year)%20and%20stay%20for%20two%20weeks%20per%20visit.%20This%20rule%20will%20be%20scrapped%20soon%20and%20the%20border%20will%20fenced%2C%20a%20senior%20government%20official%20told%20PTI%20this%20week%2C%20adding%20the%20fencing%20will%20be%20completed%20within%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20been%20one%20of%20those%20most%20vocal%20for%20the%20fencing%20and%20for%20the%20FMR%20to%20be%20scrapped%20and%20also%20for%20redeployment%20of%20security%20personnel%20to%20the%20border%20rather%20than%20within%20Indian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20has%20a%20390%20km-long%20border%20with%20Myanmar%2C%20of%20which%20only%2010%20km%20has%20been%20fenced%20so%20far.%20In%20July%2C%20the%20state%20said%20around%20700%20illegal%20immigrant