dia-news%2Fn-biren-singh-ndtv-interview-india-myanmar-border-free-movement-regime-if-there-was-border-fencing-manipur-chief-ministers-jab-on-free-movement-regime-4821246%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bilkis%20Bano's%20Rapists'%20Release%20Cancelled%3A%20What%20Supreme%20Court%20Said%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHolding%20Bilkis%20Bano's%20request%20challenging%20the%20remission%20as%20maintainable%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20BV%20Nagarathna%20and%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20said%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20was%20not%20the%20appropriate%20government%20to%20pass%20the%20remission%20order%20as%20the%20trial%20was%20held%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGujarat%20government%20should%20have%20filed%20a%20plea%20seeking%20review%20of%20the%202022%20order%20stating%20they%20aren't%20the%20competent%20government.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20exemption%20order%20lacks%20competence%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said.%20Criminals%20can%20be%20released%20only%20by%20the%20state%20where%20they%20are%20tried%2C%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20rule%20of%20law%20must%20be%20preserved%20unmindful%20of%20the%20ripples%20of%20the%20consequences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20the%20victim's%20rights%20are%20important%20and%20that%20women%20deserve%20respect.%20%26quot%3BA%20woman%20deserves%20respect%20howsoever%20high%20or%20low%20she%20may%20otherwise%20be%20considered%20in%20society%20or%20to%20whatever%20faith%20she%20may%20follow%20or%20whatever%20creed%20she%20she%20may%20belong%20to.%20Can%20heinous%20crimes%20against%20women%20permit%20remission%3F%20These%20are%20the%20issue%20which%20arise%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Nagarathna%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20came%20down%20heavily%20against%20its%20own%20judgment%20in%20May%202022%2C%20delivered%20by%20Justice%20Ajay%20Rastogi%20(retired)%2C%20which%20allowed%20the%20c