sed%20LSD%2C%20cocaine%2C%20ecstasy%2C%20and%20psychedelic%20mushrooms%20typically%20at%20parties%2C%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Musk's%20lawyer%20Alex%20Spiro%20responded%20to%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Ereport%2C%20and%20said%20that%20the%20article%20was%20reporting%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20facts%26quot%3B.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20tech%20billionaire%20agreed%20to%20undergo%20random%20drug%20testing%20for%20three%20years%20after%20his%20appearance%20on%20the%20Joe%20Rogan%20podcast%20in%202018%2C%20where%20the%2052-year-old%20was%20seen%20smoking%20marijuana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20reply%20to%20a%20post%20mentioning%20the%20WSJ%20report%2C%20Mr.%20Musk%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20''After%20that%20one%20puff%20with%20Rogan%2C%20I%20agreed%2C%20at%20NASA's%20request%2C%20to%20do%203%20years%20of%20random%20drug%20testing.%20Not%20even%20trace%20quantities%20were%20found%20of%20any%20drugs%20or%20alcohol.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAfter%20that%20one%20puff%20with%20Rogan%2C%20I%20agreed%2C%20at%20NASA's%20request%2C%20to%20do%203%20years%20of%20random%20drug%20testing.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnNot%20even%20trace%20quantities%20were%20found%20of%20any%20drugs%20or%20alcohol.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWSJ%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40WSJ%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20fit%20to%20line%20a%20parrot%20cage%20for%20bird%20%F0%9F%92%A9%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1743966490917794153%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%207%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20hit%20the%20headlines%20after%20he%20smoked%20weed%20on%20Joe%20Rogan's%20podcast%20in%202018.%20He%20later%20downplayed%20the%20incident%2C%20saying%20he%20only%20took%20'one%20puff'.%C2%A0%20The%20incident%20led%20the%20Pentagon%20to%20review%20his%20federal%20security%20clearance%2C%20which%20was%20tied%20to%20his%20company%20SpaceX's%20work%20with%20the%20U.S.%20Air%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20biographer%20Walter%20Isaacson%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BSpaceX%20was%20a%C2%A0NASA%C2%A0contractor%2C%20and%20they%20are%20big%20believers%20in%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20told%20Isaacson.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20had%20to%20be%20subjected%20to%20random%20drug%20tests%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years.%20Fortunately%2C%20I%20don't%20like%20doing%20illegal%20drugs.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20Tesla%20CEO%20has%20admitted%20to%20taking%20ketamine%2C%20a%20dissociative%20drug%20to%20treat%20depression.%C2%A0According%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fsilicon-valley-microdosing-ketamine-lsd-magic-mushrooms-d381e214%3Fmod%3Dhp_lead_pos7%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EMr%20Musk%20told%20friends%20he%20%E2%80%9Cmicrodoses%E2%80%9D%20the%20drug%2C%20taking%20small%20amounts%20to%20help%20manage%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKetamine%2C%20an%20anesthetic%20that%20has%20some%20hallucinogenic%20effects%2C%20is%20a%20controlled%20substance%20in%20the%20US%20and%20can%20only%20be%20legally%20administered%20by%20a%20medical%20professional.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20any%20form%20of%20illegal%20drug%20usage%20would%20violate%20corporate%20regulations%20at%20both%20SpaceX%20and%20Tesla%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20breaking%20federal%20contracts.%20It%20would%20also%20cast%20doubt%20on%20Musk's%20leadership%20role%20at%20the%20publicly%20listed%20Tesla%2C%20where%20the%20board%20is%20tasked%20with%20monitoring%20management%20on%20behalf%20of%20shareholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%20data-auto-link%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20data-is-watch-more%3D%5C%2