%20that%20led%20to%20a%20dramatic%20purge%20of%20top%20officials%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-01-06%2Fus-intelligence-shows-flawed-china-missiles-led-xi-jinping-to-purge-military%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20US%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2C%20which%20did%20not%20name%20its%20sources%2C%20reported%20on%20Saturday%20that%20the%20intelligence%20indicates%20Chinese%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxi-jinping-military-purge-china-disrupt-us-race-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EXi%20Jinping's%20recent%20ousting%20of%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20senior%20commanders%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20stemmed%20from%20serious%20issues%20of%20graft%20like%20these.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20purge%20went%20so%20far%20as%20to%20axe%20even%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-sacked-defense-minister-without-explanation-months-after-disappearance-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChinese%20Defense%20Minister%2C%20Li%20Shangfu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20disappeared%20for%20two%20months%20before%20being%20replaced%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorruption%20was%20so%20severe%20in%20China's%20Rocket%20Force%20and%20the%20wider%20PLA%20that%20it%20will%20likely%20force%20Xi%20to%20recalibrate%20whether%20Beijing%20can%20take%20on%20any%20major%20military%20action%20soon%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported%2C%20citing%20US%20intelligence%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Rocket%20Force%20is%20China's%20main%20military%20branch%20overseeing%20its%20nuclear%20weapons%2C%20and%20has%20been%20a%20key%20focus%20of%20Xi's%20recent%20push%20to%20modernize%20Beijing's%20forces%20rapidly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20especially%20central%20to%20China's%20posturing%20on%20Taiwan%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fmilitary%2Farticle%2F3228