thargy%20and%20a%20feeling%20of%20being%20discriminated%20against%20by%20the%20system%2C%20the%20community%2C%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20has%20taken%20to%20appearing%20for%20secular%20competitive%20examinations%20in%20a%20big%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes%20in%20Part%20VII%2C%20the%20last%20section%20of%20the%20book%2C%20%E2%80%98Finding%20Their%20Voice%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20paints%20a%20clear%2C%20searing%20picture%20of%20a%20community%20increasingly%20under%20siege%20from%20Hindutva%20forces%20that%20have%20overrun%20large%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20and%20seek%20to%20convert%20a%20once%20aspirational%20nation%20into%20a%20scapegoat-hunting%2C%20bloodthirsty%20mob%20that%20thinks%20with%20its%20fangs.%20From%20the%20mob%20lynchings%20and%20destruction%20of%20mosques%20to%20the%20distortion%20of%20history%20and%20calls%20for%20genocide%3B%20from%20the%20shockingly%20clumsy%20blaming%20of%20a%20spiritual%20conference%20for%20the%20spread%20of%20Covid-19%20in%20India%20to%20the%20data%20from%20the%20Kumbh%20Mela%20that%20actually%20became%20a%20superspreader%3B%20from%20the%20Northeast%20Delhi%20violence%20of%202020%20to%20the%20so-called%20hijab%20controversy%3B%20and%20the%20non-stop%20frenzied%2C%20partisan%20contribution%20of%20the%20mainstream%20media%20channels%20and%20publications%E2%80%A6each%20sordid%20episode%20finds%20its%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20318px)%2085vw%2C%20318px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08090124%2FIMG_4887.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22318%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08090124%2FIMG_4887.jpeg%20765w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08090124%2FIMG_4887-191x300.jpeg%20191w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08090124%2FIMG_4887-653x1024.jpeg%20653w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691973%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22499%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EZiya%20Us%20Salam%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EBeing%20Muslim%20in%20Hindu%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EHarperCollins%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20%3Cem%3EBeing%20Muslim%20in%20Hindu%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0represents%20a%20damning%20compilation%20of%20atrocities%20against%20the%20psyche%20and%20person%20of%20Indian%20Muslims%20during%20the%20nearly%20two%20terms%20of%20BJP%2FNDA%20rule%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20several%20Indian%20states%2C%20the%20author%20is%20crystal%20clear%20in%20stating%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20are%20not%20the%20only%20political%20parties%20to%20bring%20a%20communal%20taint%20to%20Indian%20polity%2C%20even%20if%20their%20communalism%20is%20of%20the%20most%20brazen%20kind.%20He%20points%20out%20the%20lack%20of%20genuine%20secular%20concern%20exhibited%20by%20other%20political%20parties%2C%20particularly%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20ruled%20India%20for%20decades%2C%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20with%20its%20massive%20majority%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Part%201%2C%20%E2%80%98Political%20Marginalisation%E2%80%99%2C%20for%20example%2C%20he%20mentions%20not%20just%20the%20disappearing%20names%20of%20Muslim%20voters%20and%20minuscule%20number%20of%20Muslim%20MPs%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20the%20proportion%20of%20the%20population%2C%20but%20also%20the%20controversial%20delimitation%20of%20constituencies%20whereby%20Muslim%20candidates%20with%20a%20high%20chance%20of%20winning%20have%20been%20unable%20to%20run%20for%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20a%20lot%20has%20been%20said%20about%20the%20political%20marginalization%20of%20Muslims%20since%202014%2C%20what%20often%20slips%20under%20the%20radar%20is%20the%20reality%20that%20since%20the%201980%20elections%2C%20Muslim%20representation%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20has%20either%20been%20declining%20or%20at%20best%20stayed%20stagnant%20even%20as%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20share%20in%20the%20general%20population%20went%20up%E2%80%A6%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20writes%20on%20page%2011.%20And%20in%20%E2%80%98Reconstituting%20Constituencies%E2%80%99%20he%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20a%20new%20development%3B%20it%20has%20been%20going%20on%20since%20Independence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20author%20calls%20out%20AAP%20more%20than%20once%2C%20as%20on%20page%20154%3A%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6Arvind%20Kejriwal%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%20taunted%20the%20Central%20government%E2%80%99s%20perceived%20inability%20to%20clear%20the%20Shaheen%20Bagh%20protest%20site%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%98We%20would%20have%20cleared%20the%20area%20within%20two%20hours.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20does%20not%20fail%20to%20remark%20how%20the%20opposition%20parties%E2%80%99%20silence%20on%20various%20issues%20has%20made%20obvious%20their%20fear%20of%20offending%20the%20perceived%20majority%20of%20Hindutva-inclined%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Salam%E2%80%99s%20other%20books%20documenting%20the%20rise%20of%20Hindu%20fundamentalism%20in%20India%2C%20primarily%20from%202014%20to%20the%20present%2C%20the%20narrative%20is%20hard-hitting%20yet%20mild%2C%20laced%20at%20times%20with%20a%20subtle%20sarcasm%2C%20at%20others%20with%20the%20authority%20of%20a%20writer%20who%20has%20the%20facts%20at%20his%20fingertips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chapters%20in%20Part%20II%2C%20%E2%80%98Rubbishing%20Medieval%20History%E2%80%99%2C%20are%20a%20refresher%20course%20for%20those%20familiar%20with%20the%20chronicles%20of%20Mughal%20India%2C%20and%20a%20compelling%20introduction%20for%20others.%20Take%20for%20instance%20Emperor%20Akbar%E2%80%99s%20Ibadat%20Khana%20in%20Agra%2C%20a%20space%20for%20debates%20and%20discussion%20among%20scholars%20of%20various%20faiths%2C%20and%20his%20policy%20of%20Sulh-i-Kul%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccan%20be%20seen%20in%20many%20ways%20as%20a%20preceptor%20to%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20which%20gives%20every%20citizen%20the%20right%20to%20equality%20and%20the%20freedom%20to%20practise%20and%20propagate%20any%20religion%E2%80%9D.%20The%20author%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20medieval%20India%2C%20where%20the%20faith%20of%20the%20emperor%20often%20determined%20the%20faith%20of%20the%20subjects%2C%20Akbar%E2%80%99s%20was%20a%20revolutionary%20move.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Aurangzeb%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwidely%20reviled%20for%20demolishing%20temples%20and%20imposing%20jizya%20(a%20discriminatory%20tax%20imposed%20on%20Hindus)%2C%E2%80%9D%20writes%20the%20author%2C%20%E2%80%9Cgave%20grants%20to%20more%20temples%20than%20he%20demolished%2C%20and%20gave%20employment%20to%20more%20non-Muslims%20than%20any%20of%20his%20predecessors.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20makes%20the%20point%20that%20for%20the%20Mughals%2C%20as%20for%20all%20rulers%20through%20history%2C%20religious%20domination%20was%20not%20the%20agenda.%20Rather%2C%20%E2%80%9C%5Bthe%5D%20social%20alliances%2C%20rifts%2C%20bonds%20and%20dissensions%20were%20all%20about%20political%20gains%20or%20losses%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20information%20helps%20balance%20the%20barrage%20of%20ill%20informed%20%E2%80%98Mughal%20bashing%E2%80%99%20that%20overloads%20social%20media%20feeds%20and%20has%20largely%20captured%20the%20gullible%20public%E2%80%99s%20imagination.%20The%20author%20is%20equipped%20to%20discuss%20the%20subject%2C%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20history%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Delhi%2C%20nearly%20three%20decades%20experience%20in%20print%20journalism%2C%20and%20a%20sharp%20ability%20to%20rebut%20the%20innumerable%20historical%20falsehoods%20propagated%20by%20those%20who%2C%20as%20he%20writes%20on%20page%20276%2C%20intend%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdemonization%20of%20an%20entire%20community%2C%20with%20no%20exceptions%E2%80%9D%2C%20seeking%20to%20blame%20today%E2%80%99s%20common%20Muslim%20for%20the%20excesses%20of%20some%20Mughal%20rulers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalam%20is%20also%20a%20former%20film%20critic.%20A%20large%20part%20of%20his%20work%20has%20been%20as%20a%20features%20editor%20and%20writer.%20Years%20of%20observing%20commercial%20Hindi%20cinema%20have%20no%20doubt%20given%20him%20a%20perspective%20on%20Indian%20society%20and%20its%20changing%20mores%20over%20the%20decades.%20The%20feature%20writing%20explains%20his%20flair%20and%20his%20love%20for%20the%20occasional%20wordplay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20among%20the%20grim%20and%20often%20tragic%20events%20detailed%20in%20this%20book%2C%20he%20manages%20to%20bring%20out%20the%20rare%20chuckle.%20Take%20the%20mention%20of%20BJP%20leader%20Sangeet%20Som%20(in%20the%20chapter%20%E2%80%98The%20Politics%20of%20Love%20Jihad%20and%20Ghar%20Wapasi%E2%80%99).%20%E2%80%9CHe%20once%20credited%20Mughal%20emperor%20Aurangzeb%20with%20building%20the%20Taj%20Mahal.%20As%20reported%20by%20Business%20Standard%2C%20%E2%80%98Som%20has%20questioned%20Taj%20Mahal%E2%80%99s%20place%20in%20history%2C%20distorting%20historical%20facts%20to%20say%20that%20it%20was%20built%20by%20an%20emperor%20who%20had%20imprisoned%20his%20father%20and%20targeted%20Hindus.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%20Then%20comes%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20cryptic%20comment.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20unaccustomed%20is%20he%20to%20ways%20of%20love!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20author%2C%20a%20practising%20Muslim%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20India%2C%20sometimes%20mentions%20his%20own%20and%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20experiences.%20These%20moments%20highlight%20the%20uncommon%20strength%20required%20to%20document%20the%20current%20troubled%20times%2C%20maintaining%20perspective%20even%20when%20under%20personal%20attack.%20The%20pain-filled%20narrative%20gives%20rise%20to%20a%20suffocating%20shame%20in%20those%20of%20us%20born%20into%20the%20majority%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20can%20an%20Indian%20reader%2C%20belonging%20to%20any%20faith%2C%20not%20read%20it%20with%20an%20urgent%20acknowledgment%20of%20personal%20stakes%3F%20The%20nation%20that%20won%20independence%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20secularism%20and%20multiculturalism%2C%20with%20a%20mind-boggling%20array%20of%20languages%2C%20food%20traditions%2C%20dress%2C%20customs%20and%20arts%2C%20a%20democracy%20(even%20if%20flawed)%20of%20breathtaking%20cultural%20variety%2C%20is%20being%20congealed%20into%20a%20monolith.%20Within%2075%20years%20of%20independence.%20And%20the%20silent%20majority%20is%20watching%20it%20happen.%20Can%20any%20of%20us%20declare%20ourselves%20unconcerned%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20slim%20and%20well%20organised%20volume%20divided%20into%20seven%20parts%2C%20each%20part%20containing%20some%20two%20to%20six%20brief%20chapters%2C%20%3Cem%3EBeing%20Muslim%20in%20Hindu%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0is%20among%20the%20most%20important%20publications%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20suffers%20from%20a%20big%20drawback%20for%20which%20the%20publishers%20are%20responsible%3A%20The%20detailed%20notes%20citing%20textual%2C%20news%20and%20interview%20sources%20are%20not%20included%20in%20the%20print%20edition.%20All%20one%20finds%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3ENotes%3C%2Fem%3E%20page%20is%20a%20scannable%20QR%20code%20to%20access%20the%20material%20on%20the%20HarperCollins%20website.%20This%20inconvenient%20arrangement%20is%20a%20disservice%20to%20a%20book%20of%20such%20a%20serious%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20read%2C%20whether%20with%20a%20paperback%20in%20one%20hand%20and%20a%20smartphone%20in%20the%20other%2C%20or%20on%20a%20Kindle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%202024%20be%20a%20year%20of%20contemplation%20and%20redressal%2C%20a%20year%20of%20reading%20genuinely%20sourced%20material.%20A%20real%20new%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fanjana-rajan%5C%22%3EAnjana%20Rajan%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0has%20been%20writing%20on%20the%20arts%2C%20literature%20and%20society%20for%20nearly%2020%20years.%20She%20is%20a%20former%20deputy%20editor%20of%C2%A0%3C%2