C%20Breivik's%20lawyer%20wrote%20in%20a%20filing%20to%20Oslo%20district%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20now%20suicidal%2C%26quot%3B%20Oeystein%20Storrvik%20added.%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20now%20dependent%20on%20the%20depression%20medicine%20Prozac%20to%20get%20through%20the%20days%20in%20prison.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawyers%20representing%20the%20justice%20ministry%20say%20Breivik%20must%20be%20kept%20apart%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20prison%20population%20because%20of%20the%20continuing%20security%20threat%20he%20poses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20in%20their%20court%20filing%20his%20isolation%20was%20%26quot%3Brelative%26quot%3B%20given%20he%20has%20contacts%20with%20guards%2C%20a%20priest%2C%20health%20professionals%20and%2C%20until%20recently%2C%20an%20outside%20volunteer%20whom%20Breivik%20no%20longer%20wishes%20to%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20sees%20two%20inmates%20for%20an%20hour%20every%20other%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EControl%20over%20Breivik's%20contacts%20with%20the%20outside%20world%20is%20justified%20by%20the%20risk%20that%20will%20inspire%20others%20to%20commit%20violent%20acts%2C%20the%20lawyers%20argue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpecifically%2C%20this%20applies%20to%20contacts%20with%20far-right%20circles%2C%20including%20people%20who%20wish%20to%20establish%20contact%20with%20Breivik%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20terrorist%20acts%20on%2022%20July%202011%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20in%20the%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreivik%20was%20cited%20as%20an%20inspiration%20by%20Brenton%20Tarrant%2C%20who%20killed%2051%20people%20in%20two%20mosques%20in%20Christchurch%2C%20New%20Zealand%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreivik%20serving%20a%2021-year%20sentence%20-%20the%20longest%20a%20Norwegian%20court%20can%20impose%20-%20which%20can%20be%20extended%20for%20as%20long%20as%20he%20is%20deemed%20a%20threat%20to%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20unique%20is%20how%20long%20he%20has%20been%20in%20