es.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndependent%20candidates%20took%2052%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20Jatiya%20Party%2C%20the%20third%C2%A0largest%20in%20the%20country%2C%20took%2011%20seats.%20The%20results%20for%20the%20rest%20of%C2%A0the%20constituencies%20were%20still%20trickling%20in%20late%20on%20Sunday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20has%20been%20slow%20to%20announce%20the%20results%20of%20the%20elections.%20The%20polls%20closed%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20with%20a%20significantly%20low%20turnout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20know%20about%20the%20vote%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20in%20the%20country%20of%20about%20170%20million%20people%20began%20at%208%20a.m.%20local%20time%20(0200%20GMT%2FUTC)%20and%20lasted%20until%205%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurnout%20was%20about%2040%25%20when%20polls%20closed%2C%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20Kazi%20Habibul%20Awal%20said.%20The%20last%20election%20in%202018%20saw%20almost%20twice%20as%20many%20voters%20turn%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%202%2C000%20candidates%20are%20competing%20for%20300%20directly%20elected%20parliamentary%20seats.%20There%20are%20436%20independent%20candidates%2C%20the%20most%20since%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresiding%20officer%20Prashun%20Goswami%20told%20AFP%20news%20agency%20that%20a%20couple%20hours%20after%20voting%20began%2C%20only%20111%20people%20had%20cast%20ballots%20out%20of%20the%20nearly%204%2C200%20registered%20at%20one%20polling%20station%20in%20Dhaka%E2%80%99s%20west.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20concerns%20about%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fbangladesh-several-arrested-over-train-fire-on-election-eve%2Fa-67904583%5C%22%3Eviolence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20voter%20turnout%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20low.%20Troops%20and%20other%20security%20forces%20have%20been%20deployed%20across%20the%20country%20to%20guard%20polling%20booths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBangladesh%20faces%20turbulence%20as%20opposition%20questions%20credibility%20of%20elections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20period%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20elections%20has%20been%20marred%20by%20protests%20in%20the%20country%20affected%20by%20economic%20slowdown%2C%20human%20rights%20violations%20and%20a%20crackdown%20on%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20seven%20opposition%20members%20were%20arrested%20after%20a%20train%20was%20set%20on%20fire%20in%20Dhaka%20in%20suspected%20arson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20Bangladesh%20Nationalist%20Party%20(BNP)%20and%20some%20of%20its%20smaller%20allies%20have%20boycotted%20the%20elections%2C%20questioning%20their%20credibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20called%20for%20a%20two-day%20nationwide%20strike%20from%20Saturday%2C%20and%20urged%20Hasina%E2%80%99s%20resignation%2C%20along%20with%C2%A0the%20setting%20up%20of%20a%20neutral%20authority%20to%20conduct%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BNP%20is%20a%20terrorist%20organisation.%20I%20am%20trying%20my%20best%20to%20ensure%20that%20democracy%20should%20continue%20in%20this%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hasina%20told%20reporters%20after%20casting%20her%20vote%20on%20Sunday%20at%20City%20College%20in%20Dhaka%2C%20accompanied%20by%20her%20daughter%20and%20other%20members%20of%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20says%20Hasina%E2%80%99s%20Awami%20League%20has%20propped%20up%20%E2%80%9Cdummy%E2%80%9D%20candidates%20as%20independent%20contesters%20to%20make%20the%20elections%20look%20fair.%20The%20main%20opposition%20leader%20Khaleda%20Zia%20is%20effectively%20under%20house%20arrest%2C%20under%20corruption%20charges%20that%20she%20claims%20are%20false.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHasina%20denies%20opposition%20accusations%2C%20says%20rivals%20fueled%20violent%20demos%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitics%20in%20the%20nation%20has%20been%20polarized%20by%20the%20rivalry%20between%20the%20two%20powerful%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZia%E2%