nt%20with%20hardly%20any%20discussion%2C%20and%20that%20too%20after%20144%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20belonging%20to%20several%20opposition%20parties%20were%20suspended%20following%20their%20protest%20when%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20did%20not%20make%20a%20statement%20in%20the%20Parliament%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20breach%20of%20security%20committed%20by%20some%20youth%20who%20trespassed%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber%20and%20released%20gas%20from%20a%20canister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BNS%20provided%20a%20legal%20structure%20to%20make%20drivers%20culpable%20in%20cases%20of%20death%2C%20not%20amounting%20homicide%2C%20caused%20by%20rash%20and%20negligent%20driving%20and%20prescribed%2010%20years%20of%20imprisonment%20or%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%207%20lakh%20for%20those%20offenders%20who%20flee%20the%20accident%20site%20without%20reporting%20the%20incident%20to%20designated%20authorities.%20This%20new%20penalty%20is%20far%20higher%20than%20the%20two-year%20imprisonment%20prescribed%20in%20the%20IPC%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20was%20resented%20by%20truck%20drivers%20who%20protested%20against%20the%20stringent%20penal%20provision%20across%20the%20nation%20and%20paralysed%20the%20supply%20chain%20when%20the%20trucks%20and%20lorries%20they%20were%20driving%20came%20to%20stand%20still%20following%20their%20countrywide%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHome%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20statement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReckoning%20that%20the%20strike%20has%20caused%20a%20grave%20crisis%20by%20seriously%20disrupting%20the%20supply%20of%20essential%20items%20across%20the%20country%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20secretary%20had%20parleys%20with%20the%20striking%20drivers%20and%20their%20representatives%20on%20January%202%20and%20issued%20a%20statement.%20While%20taking%20cognisance%20of%20the%20concerns%20of%20truckers%20regarding%20the%20provision%20of%2010%20years%20imprisonment%20and%20fine%2C%20under%20Section%20106%20(2)%20of%20BNS%2C%20it%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20these%20new%20laws%20and%20provisions%20have%20not%20yet%20come%20into%20force%20and%20the%20decision%20to%20invoke%20that%20section%20will%20be%20taken%20only%20after%20consultation%20with%20the%20All%20India%20Motor%20Transport%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20this%20unambiguously%20brings%20out%20the%20crucial%20point%20that%20the%20lawmaking%20process%20anchored%20in%20deliberative%20and%20consultative%20method%20had%20not%20been%20followed%20by%20the%20Modi%20regime%20before%20it%20was%20taken%20up%20in%20the%20Parliament.%20Had%20the%20deliberative%20and%20consultative%20process%20been%20followed%20by%20the%20powers%20that%20be%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20would%20have%20engaged%20itself%20with%20the%20association%20of%20drivers%20or%20their%20representatives%20to%20ascertain%20their%20views%20on%20those%20stringent%20measures%20to%20deal%20with%20rash%20and%20negligent%20driving.%20Tragically%2C%20the%20consultation%20is%20now%20going%20to%20take%20place%20after%20the%20law%20has%20been%20enacted%20following%20the%20assent%20it%20has%20got%20from%20the%20President%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Second%20Avatar%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Law%20Bills%3A%20The%20Key%20Changes%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsecond-avatar-criminal-law-bills-has-anything-changed%5C%22%3ESecond%20Avatar%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Law%20Bills%3A%20The%20Key%20Changes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMinimum%20government%20and%20maximum%20governance%20exposed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20regime%2C%20which%20often%20claimed%20that%20it%20would%20ushering%20in%20the%20era%20of%20%E2%80%98minimum%20government%20and%20maximum%20governance%E2%80%99%2C%20has%20dispensed%20with%20the%20process%20of%20deliberation%20and%20consultation%20for%20framing%20laws%20which%20remain%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20governance.%20It%20is%20quite%20sad%20that%20legislations%20are%20taken%20up%20in%20Parliament%20without%20referring%20most%20of%20these%20to%20the%20department-related%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committees%20for%20scrutiny%20and%20examination%20on%20a%20bipartisan%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bills%20are%20now%20passed%20without%20adequate%20discussion%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20both%20the%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%20and%20thereby%20not%20generating%20the%20legislative%20intent%20behind%20those%20Bills%20which%20get%20enacted%20eventually%20by%20employing%20majority%20strength%20of%20the%20ruling%20party.%20It%20is%20well%20known%20that%20Bills%20are%20framed%20by%20government%20departments%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20these%20represent%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20intent.%20When%20those%20Bills%20are%20adequately%20discussed%20in%20both%20the%20Houses%20of%20the%20Parliament%20and%20its%20clauses%20are%20scrutinised%20and%20debated%2C%20the%20legislative%20intent%20of%20the%20apex%20legislature%20is%20expressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20rather%20unfortunate%20that%20when%20the%20BNS%20was%20taken%20up%20for%20discussion%2C%20hardly%20two%20hours%20were%20allotted%20for%20discussion%20on%20a%20measure%20which%20aimed%20at%20fundamentally%20altering%20the%20criminal%20code.%20By%20doing%20away%20with%20the%20deliberative%20and%20consultative%20process%20of%20law%20making%2C%20the%20views%20and%20interests%20of%20stakeholders%20are%20lost%20sight%20of%20and%20it%20results%20in%20the%20imposition%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20intent%20on%20the%20citizenry%2C%20who%20are%20hardly%20persuaded%20to%20follow%20that%20law%20in%20the%20making%20of%20which%20they%20had%20no%20role.%20Exactly%20the%20same%20thing%20happened%20to%20four%20farm%20laws%2C%20which%20were%20enacted%20by%20the%20Modi%20regime%20in%202020%20without%20consulting%20the%20farmers%20and%20their%20unions%2C%20and%20only%20after%20the%20massive%20year%20long%20movement%20of%20farmers%20against%20those%20laws%20did%20the%20government%20eventually%20concede%20to%20the%20demand%20of%20farmers%20for%20their%20repeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20repeal%20of%20the%20farm%20laws%20and%20now%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20that%20the%20section%20of%20BNS%20dealing%20with%20stringent%20punishment%20for%20drivers%20would%20not%20be%20implemented%20without%20consulting%20them%20clearly%20shows%20that%20the%20law%20making%20process%20followed%20by%20Modi%20regime%20is%20seriously%20flawed%2C%20as%20it%20is%20based%20on%20the%20crude%20majority%20it%20has%20in%20Parliament%20and%20not%20founded%20on%20a%20deliberative%20and%20consultative%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20warning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2016%2C%201948%2C%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20had%20thoughtfully%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20Cabinet%20worthy%20of%20being%20representative%20of%20a%20large%20mass%20of%20mankind%20can%20afford%20to%20take%20any%20step%20merely%20because%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20win%20the%20hasty%20applause%20of%20an%20unthinking%20public.%20In%20the%20midst%20of%20insanity%2C%20should%20not%20our%20best%20representatives%20retain%20sanity%20and%20bravely%20prevent%20a%20wreck%20of%20the%20ship%20of%20State%20under%20their%20management%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restoration%20of%20sanity%20and%20its%20retention%20lies%20in%20restoring%20the%20deliberative%20and%20consultative%20process%20of%20law%20making%20to%20%E2%80%9Cprevent%20a%20wreck%20of%20the%20ship%20of%20State%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20Sahu%20served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%20K.R.%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704677457000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24153155%2FF6ZBJaLbwAANsqu-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftruckers-strike-exposes-how-hollow-a-law-passed-without-consultation-is%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20lesson%20should%20already%20have%20been%20learnt%20from%20the%20contentious%20farm%20laws%20and%20their%20repeal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftruckers-strike-exposes-how-hollow-a-law-passed-without-consultation-is%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20sexual%20assault%20in%20the%20metaverse%20has%20investigators%20questioning%20the%20future%20of%20virtual%20crime%20prosecution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225734%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20plays%20a%20video%20game%20using%20a%20virtual-reality%20headset%20at%20an%20arcade.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659b2b0c1c5c7b8c9a0ea865%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223823%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20UK%20police%20are%20investigating%20a%20teenage%20girl's%20claim%20that%20her%20avatar%20was%20digitally%20gang-raped%20in%20a%20virtual%20reality%20game.%3Cp%3EMATTHEW%20KNIGHT%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUK%20authorities%20are%20investigating%20the%20claim%20of%20a%20simulated%20gang%20rape%20of%20a%20teenager's%20VR%20avatar.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20teen%20told%20the%20police%20she%20was%20using%20a%20headset%20to%20play%20a%20VR%20video%20game%20when%20male%20players%20attacked%20her%20avatar.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOfficials%20say%20the%20girl%20faced%20trauma%20akin%20to%20real-life%20assault%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20others%20aren't%20so%20sure%20that's%20possible.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20teenager's%20claim%20that%20her%20avatar%20was%20gang-raped%20in%20an%20immersive%20virtual-reality%20game%20is%20being%20investigated%20by%20UK%20authorities%2C%20who%20are%20said%20to%20be%20considering%20the%20novel%20question%20of%20whether%20such%20an%20act%20in%20the%20metaverse%20can%20be%20criminally%20charged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20girl%2C%20who%20was%20identified%20only%20as%20being%20under%20the%20age%20of%2016%2C%20was%20wearing%20a%20VR%20headset%20to%20play%20online%20when%20several%20male%20players%20attacked%20and%20%26quot%3Bgang-raped%26quot%3B%20her%20digital%20avatar%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-12917329%2FPolice-launch-investigation-kind-virtual-rape-metaverse.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBritish%20police%20sources%20told%20%3Cu%3EThe%20Daily%20Mail%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20she%20was%20not%20physically%20injured%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported%20the%20girl%20was%20deeply%20distraught%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20and%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20familiar%20with%20the%20case%20told%20The%20Daily%20Mail%20she%20experienced%20trauma%20similar%20to%20a%20real-life%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDonna%20Jones%2C%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20Association%20of%20Police%20and%20Crime%20Commissioners%2C%20confirmed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-67865327%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20BBC%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20incident%20was%20first%20reported%20to%20authorities%20in%202023%2C%20triggering%20an%20investigation%20by%20police.%20Still%2C%20BBC%20could%20not%20verify%20which%20force%20launched%20the%20probe%20into%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20how%20the%20British%20police%20ultimately%20decide%20to%20handle%20the%20incident%2C%20law%20enforcement%2C%20and%20safety%20researchers%20say%20concerns%20over%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20violence%20in%20the%20metaverse%20need%20to%20be%20addressed%20as%20virtual%20and%20augmented%20reality%20technology%20becomes%20more%20convincing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVR%20goggles%20cover%20users'%20peripheral%20vision%20to%20create%20an%20immersive%20experience.%20Depending%20on%20user%20settings%2C%20players%20may%20experience%20vibrations%20in%20their%20handheld%20controls%20when%20experiencing%20in-game%20stimuli.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20users%20who%20find%20their%20characters%20in%20precarious%20in-game%20situations%20involving%20other%20player-controlled%20characters%20may%20not%20be%20under%20direct%20physical%20threat%2C%20researchers%20say%20the%20immersive%20nature%20of%20a%20VR%20experience%20can%20heighten%20the%20emotional%20response%20to%20the%20content%20presented%20through%20goggles%20or%20sensations%20registered%20through%20haptic%20suits.%20These%20touch-sensitive%20full-body%20suits%20vibrate%20in%20response%20to%20virtual%20stimuli%2C%20reacting%20when%20users'%20characters%20bump%20into%20a%20wall%20or%20receive%20a%20punch%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn-game%20actions%20with%20a%20psychological%20toll%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20boosters%20of%20this%20technology%20cannot%20have%20it%20both%20ways%2C%26quot%3B%20Katherine%20Cross%2C%20who%20researches%20online%20harassment%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Washington%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThey%20cannot%20tout%20the%20realism%20of%20these%20virtual%20worlds%20and%20then%20deny%20or%20downplay%20that%20ugly%20things%20that%20happen%20in%20them%20have%20some%20of%20the%20unfortunate%20downstream%20effects%20of%20real%20behavior.%20If%20it's%20real%20enough%20to%20be%20marketable%20in%20a%20unique%20way%2C%20it's%20real%20enough%20for%20there%20to%20be%20social%20consequences%20and%20psychological%20consequences%20when%20something%20goes%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECross%20said%20the%20core%20of%20VR%20technology%20relies%20on%20tricking%20a%20user's%20brain%20at%20a%20fundamental%20level%20into%20thinking%20that%20they're%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ephysically%20experiencing%20the%20things%20on%20screen%20by%20mimicking%20sensations%20experienced%20in%20the%20real%20world%2C%20like%20walking%20through%20space%20or%20swimming.%20That%20trickery%20of%20the%20brain%20is%20why%2C%20she%20says%2C%20users%20can%20sometimes%20feel%20a%20bit%20disoriented%20for%20a%20few%20seconds%20once%20they%20take%20the%20headset%20off%20and%20realize%20they're%20still%20standing%20in%20their%20living%20room%20or%20on%20a%20convention%20show%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20what%20that%20means%20is%20that%20if%20something%20potentially%20traumatic%20happens%20in%20that%20space%2C%20you%20may%20immediately%2C%20or%20almost%20immediately%2C%20consciously%20realize%20it's%20just%20a%20game%20and%20this%20isn't%20really%20happening%2C%20but%20there's%20that%20moment%20where%20your%20lizard%20brain%20sort%20of%20has%20to%20catch%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Cross%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20not%20unreasonable%20to%20think%20that%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20trauma.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20safety%20researchers%20and%20law%20enforcement%20raising%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20potential%20real-world%20ramifications%20that%20VR%20attacks%20and%20harassment%20might%20have%2C%20the%20debate%20rages%20on%20in%20online%20forums%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FOculusQuest%2Fcomments%2F18wjpzn%2Fvirtual_reality_sexual_assault_a_discussion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EReddit%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20virtual%20sexual%20assault%2C%20with%20some%20users%20suggesting%20that%20claims%20of%20being%20traumatized%20by%20virtual%20attacks%20are%20minimizing%20%26quot%3Bactual%20rape%20victims.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fnypost%2Fp%2FC1ngIOZIBSe%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EInstagram%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20response%20to%20a%20New%20York%20Post%20article%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20users%20joked%20the%20assailants%20who%20harassed%20the%20girl%20online%20should%20be%20sent%20to%20%26quot%3Bvirtual%20jail.%26quot%3B%20Others%20quipped%20they%20were%20waiting%20for%20justice%20after%20their%20character%20in%20%26quot%3BCall%20of%20Duty%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20first-person%20shooter%20game%2C%20was%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20dismiss%20this%20as%20being%20not%20real%2C%20but%20the%20whole%20point%20of%20these%20virtual%20environments%20is%20they%20are%20incredibly%20immersive%2C%26quot%3B%20UK%20Home%20Secretary%20James%20Cleverly%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fpolice-investigate-rape-metaverse%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELBC%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20incident.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20we're%20talking%20about%20a%20child%20here%2C%20and%20a%20child%20has%20gone%20through%20sexual%20trauma.%20It%20will%20have%20had%20a%20very%20significant%20psychological%20effect%20and%20we%20should%20be%20very%2C%20very%20careful%20about%20being%20dismissive%20of%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20also%20worth%20realizing%20that%20somebody%20who%20is%20willing%20to%20put%20a%20child%20through%20a%20trauma%20like%20that%20digitally%20may%20well%20be%20someone%20that%20could%20go%20on%20to%20do%20terrible%20things%20in%20the%20physical%20realm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESexual%20harassment%20on%20'Horizon%20Worlds'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EClaims%20like%20the%20British%20girl's%20are%20not%20unheard%20of%2C%20with%20multiple%20accounts%20of%20virtual%20sexual%20harassment%20stemming%20from%20Meta's%20%26quot%3BHorizon%20Worlds%26quot%3B%20VR%20game%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0though%20it%20remains%20unclear%20if%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20inside%20Meta's%20game%20or%20another%20VR%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20a%20metaverse%20researcher%20who%20was%20studying%20user%20behavior%20on%20%26quot%3BHorizon%20Worlds%26quot%3B%20wrote%20that%20her%20avatar%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresearcher-claims-her-avatar-was-raped-on-metas-metaverse-platform-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eraped%20roughly%20an%20hour%20into%20her%20first%20session%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20part%20of%20my%20brain%20was%20like%20wtf%20is%20happening%2C%20the%20other%20part%20was%20like%20this%20isn't%20a%20real%20body%2C%20and%20another%20part%20was%20like%2C%20this%20is%20important%20research%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20researcher%20said%20in%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eko.org%2Fimages%2FMetaverse_report_May_2022.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereport%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20users%20who%20assaulted%20her%20avatar%20had%20requested%20she%20disable%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-metaverse-virtual-groping-personal-boundary-safety-bubble-horizons-venues-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E4-foot%20safety%20bubble%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20initiating%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonths%20earlier%2C%20in%202021%2C%20another%20metaverse%20researcher%20named%20Nina%20Jane%20Patel%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Medium%20that%20three%20to%20four%20male-looking%20avatars%20had%20gang-raped%20her%20avatar%20within%2060%20seconds%20after%20she%20joined%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fninajanepatel.medium.com%2Ffiction-vs-non-fiction-d824c6edfbe2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EHorizon%20Worlds%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20calling%20the%20incident%20a%20surreal%20nightmare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20girl%20involved%20is%20very%20brave%2C%26quot%3B%20Patel%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BBringing%20this%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20police%20would%20have%20been%20no%20easy%20task%2C%20and%20she%20is%20breaking%20ground%20with%20her%20actions.%C2%A0While%20we%20don't%20know%20where%20it%20will%20lead%2C%20it%20is%20a%20step%20in%20the%20right%20direction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summer%20of%202022%2C%20following%20early%20reports%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20simulated%20assault%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2022%2F7%2F22%2F23274676%2Fmeta-horizon-worlds-mature-content-18-plus-tag%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20Verge%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20Meta%20had%20expanded%20the%20acceptable%20types%20of%20content%20in%20%26quot%3BHorizon%20Worlds%26quot%3B%20to%20include%20%26quot%3Bmature%26quot%3B%20content%20for%20users%20over%20the%20age%20of%2018%2C%20including%20depictions%20of%20alcohol%2C%20tobacco%2C%20and%20marijuana%20use%20as%20well%20as%20%26quot%3Bnear%20nudity%2C%20depictions%20of%20people%20in%20implied%20or%20suggestive%20positions%2C%20or%20an%20environment%20focused%20on%20activities%20that%20are%20overly%20suggestive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%26quot%3Bnudity%2C%20depictions%20of%20people%20in%20explicit%20positions%2C%20or%20content%20or%20worlds%20that%20are%20sexually%20provocative%20or%20implied%26quot%3B%20remains%20prohibited%20in%20public%20spaces%2C%20according%20to%20Meta's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meta.com%2Fhelp%2Fquest%2Farticles%2Fhorizon%2Fcreate-in-horizon-worlds%2Frestrictions-to-worlds-in-horizon%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epolicy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20mature%20content%20on%20the%20site.%20In-game%20avatars%20are%20depicted%20from%20the%20torso%20up%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20do%20not%20have%20legs%20or%20genitals%20that%20can%20be%20seen%20while%20playing.%20However%2C%20users%20can%20simulate%20sex%20with%20provocative%20positions%20of%20their%20avatars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Meta%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20tech%20giant%20told%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2024%2F01%2F02%2Fpolice-investigate-virtual-rape-a-child-metaverse-20050890%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cu%3EMetro%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20kind%20of%20behavior%20described%20has%20no%20place%20on%20our%20platform%2C%20which%20is%20why%20for%20all%20users%2C%20we%20have%20an%20automatic%20protection%20called%20personal%20boundary%2C%20which%20keeps%20people%20you%20don't%20know%20a%20few%20feet%20away%20from%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDefining%20the%20new%20frontier%20of%20cybercrime%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20isn't%20the%20first%20sexual%20attack%20that%20has%20been%20reported%20in%20virtual%20reality%2C%20it%20is%20thought%20to%20be%20the%20first%20time%20the%20UK%20authorities%20are%20investigating%20whether%20such%20an%20attack%20can%20be%20charged%20as%20a%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatel%20told%20BI%20that%20there's%20a%20need%20for%20specific%20legislation%20that%20addresses%20the%20unique%20nature%20of%20offenses%20in%20the%20metaverse%2C%20including%20defining%20and%20criminalizing%20acts%20of%20grooming%2C%20bullying%2C%20and%20harassment%20in%20virtual%20environments.%20She%20also%20advocates%20for%20creating%20stringent%20age%20verification%20systems%2C%20privacy%20controls%2C%20and%20parental%20supervision%20tools%20tailored%20to%20the%20metaverse's%20immersive%20experience%20without%20stifling%20the%20innovation%20and%20freedom%20that%20make%20the%20alternate%20reality%20world%20compelling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProtecting%20children%20in%20the%20Metaverse%20requires%20a%20multifaceted%20approach%3A%20psychologically%20informed%20safeguards%20to%20prevent%20trauma%2C%20robust%20legal%20frameworks%20to%20define%20and%20prosecute%20offenses%2C%20and%20international%20cooperation%20to%20effectively%20enforce%20these%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20Patel%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20critical%20area%20that%20demands%20immediate%20attention%20to%20ensure%20the%20Metaverse%20is%20a%20safe%20and%20positive%20space%20for%20young%20users.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECross%2C%20however%2C%20isn't%20sure%20that%20one-size-fits-all%20legislation%20is%20the%20correct%20answer%2C%20saying%20that%20laws%20that%20criminalize%20behavior%20in%20the%20metaverse%20are%20treating%20a%20symptom%2C%20not%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20problem%20and%20that%20government%20enforcers%20%26quot%3Bmay%20not%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20the%20relief%20that%20people%20seek%20or%20deserve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%2C%20ultimately%2C%20it%20is%20on%20the%20platform%20holders%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20public%20more%20openly%20on%20these%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20Cross%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20establish%20a%20serious%20package%20of%20reforms%20that%20they%20can%20bring%20forward%20to%20empower%20users%20to%20give%20them%20organizing%20tools%2C%20not%20just%20private%20moderation%20tools%2C%20but%20the%20ability%20to%20effectively%20police%20their%20own%20communities%20and%20work%20hand%20in%20hand%20with%20an%20expanded%20moderation%20and%20trust%20and%20safety%20team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECross%20added%20that%20she%20believes%20a%20more%20effective%20arena%20of%20legislation%20would%20require%20large%20companies%20to%20have%20sufficiently%20staffed%20trust%20and%20safety%20teams%20working%20to%20address%20issues%20of%20virtual%20harassment%2C%20putting%20the%20onus%20back%20on%20the%20businesses%20rather%20than%20individuals%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20online%20and%20virtual%20reality%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20existing%20laws%20prohibit%20cybercrime%2C%20including%20fraud%2C%20harassment%2C%20and%20the%20distribution%20of%20child-sexual-abuse%20material%20online%2C%20an%20investigator%20familiar%20with%20the%20UK%20case%20told%20The%20Daily%20Mail%20they%20were%20unsure%20whether%20the%20teen's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-woman-claims-virtually-groped-metaverse-horizon-venues-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eallegation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20be%20prosecuted%20under%20current%20law%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bcurrent%20legislation%20is%20not%20set%20up%20for%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20beginning%20to%20think%20about%20what%20is%20a%20crime%20in%20the%20metaverse%20and%20how%20we%20police%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Graeme%20Biggar%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20UK's%20National%20Crime%20Agency%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.standard.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fcrime%2Frapes-murders-criminal-offences-virtual-reality-metaverse-nca-b1128084.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20Evening%20Standard%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20dominating%20our%20thinking%20because%20there%20is%20plenty%20of%20real-world%20crime%20for%20us%20to%20be%20getting%20on%20with%2C%20but%20if%20you%20are%20in%20the%20metaverse%20wearing%20a%20haptic%20suit%20where%20you%20can%20sense%20what%20is%20happening%20to%20and%20then%20you%20are%20sexually%20assaulted%2C%20raped%2C%20or%20murdered%2C%20even%20if%20you%20are%20not%20wearing%20a%20haptic%20suit%2C%20is%20that%20OK%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpolice-investigate-digital-gang-rape-teen-vr-metaverse-horizon-worlds-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704677173000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659b2b3dec62ab5daf815f86%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpolice-investigate-digital-gang-rape-teen-vr-metaverse-horizon-worlds-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20British%20police%20are%20investigating%20a%20relatively%20novel%20allegation%3A%20that%20a%20teenage%20girl's%20avatar%20was%20gang-raped%20in%20an%20immersive%20VR%20game.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpolice-investigate-digital-gang-rape-teen-vr-metaverse-horizon-worlds-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20didn't%20even%20write%2