s%20that%20the%20pateela%20of%20gosht%20has%20disappeared.%20Now%20who%20would%20steal%20the%20pateela%3F%20Somebody%20who%20is%20hungry%20and%20who%20likes%20gosht%2C%E2%80%9D%20Habib%20paused%20expectantly%2C%20waiting%20for%20an%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKanwal!%20Who%20loves%20gosht%2C%20I%20am%20sure%2C%20but%20who%20dare%20not%20eat%20it%20in%20public%20after%20having%20set%20up%20his%20little%20vigilante%20outfit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHabib%20seemed%20confused%2C%20for%20a%20moment.%20%E2%80%9CKanwal%20did%20come%20to%20the%20restaurant%20that%20evening%2C%20and%20he%20did%20eat%20his%20mutton%2C%20so%20he%20probably%20didn%E2%80%99t%20kill%20for%20the%20pateela.%20This%20has%20to%20be%20someone%20who%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20it%2C%20was%20hungry%20and%20just%20wanted%20to%20eat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHabibi%2C%20that%20is%20more%20than%20half%20the%20people%20in%20the%20gali.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20also%20someone%20who%20knew%20the%20restaurant%20enough%20to%20know%20that%20there%20would%20be%20such%20a%20pateela%20in%20the%20kitchen%3B%20and%20more%20important%2C%20somebody%20who%20knew%20Rahman%20miyan%20personally%20and%20who%20disliked%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20could%20be%20any%20of%20the%20older%20boys%20in%20the%20madarsa%2C%20Habibi.%20They%20are%20always%20hungry%20and%20in%20need%20of%20nourishment%2C%20and%20Rahman%20miyan%20was%20harsh%20to%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20thinking%20of%20Salman%2C%20who%20had%20been%20angry%20with%20Rahman%20miyan%20for%20taking%20away%20his%20room%20at%20the%20madarsa%2C%E2%80%9D%20Habib%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSalman%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20for%20food.%20His%20mother%20would%20feed%20him.%20Not%20mutton%2C%20perhaps%2C%20but%20something.%20Also%20his%20ladylove%20would%20feed%20him!%20He%20was%20just%20being%20dramatic%20about%20being%20%E2%80%98thrown%20out%E2%80%99%E2%80%93%20he%20dropped%20out%20from%20studying%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20Rahman%20miyan%20was%20continuing%20to%20lodge%20him%20at%20the%20madarsa.%20Then%20our%20hero%20would%20break%20all%20the%20rules%2C%20come%20in%20at%20all%20hours%20%E2%80%93%20anybody%20would%20have%20told%20him%20to%20vacate%20the%20room.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20as%20if%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20place%20to%20stay.%20He%20has%20always%20had%20a%20home%20with%20his%20mother.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20you%20think%20one%20of%20the%20madarsa%20boys%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20have%20been%20involved%20than%20Salman%3F%20But%2C%20Jamal%20bhai%2C%20they%20are%20so%20timid%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20them%20picking%20up%20a%20steam%20iron%20and%20assaulting%20Rahman%20miyan.%20If%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20were%20more%20passive%20%E2%80%93%20Rahman%20miyan%20had%20a%20bad%20case%20of%20wheezing%20and%20somebody%20hid%20his%20inhaler%2C%20or%20rather%20dragged%20their%20feet%20when%20sent%20to%20bring%20it%20from%20his%20home%20%E2%80%93%20then%20I%E2%80%99d%20think%20the%20boys%20might%20have%20done%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Habib%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHabibi%2C%20if%20only%20the%20sun%20came%20out%20and%20we%20had%20more%20light%20and%20less%20smog%2C%20and%20if%20our%20minds%20unfroze%20a%20bit%2C%20we%20would%20solve%20the%20mystery%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20lit%20his%20first%20cigarette%20of%20the%20day%2C%20took%20a%20drag%20and%20coughed%20the%20customary%20cough.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20you%20have%20a%20motive%20%E2%80%93%20hunger%20%E2%80%93%20but%20no%20method.%20Then%2C%20second%20theory%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20he%20was%20assaulted%20with%20his%20own%20steam%20iron%2C%20then%20that%20suggests%20a%20fight%2C%20or%20an%20argument%20that%20suddenly%20escalated.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20someone%20who%20would%20be%20arguing%20with%20him%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20not%20the%20timid%20madarsa%20boys%2C%20who%20scurried%20at%20the%20sight%20of%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20could%20the%20argument%20be%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLaadley%20is%20too%20laid%20back%20to%20argue%2C%20though%20he%20is%20strong%20enough%20to%20pick%20up%20an%20object%20and%20hit.%20But%20Rana%20and%20Kanwal%20were%20both%20there%3A%20they%E2%80%99d%20have%20teased%20and%20bullied%2C%20and%20started%20an%20argument.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20Habibi%2C%20that%20is%20very%20unlikely.%20A%20policeman%20won%E2%80%99t%20pick%20up%20a%20steam%20iron%20and%20murder%20someone%20in%20the%20heat%20of%20the%20moment%2C%20yaar.%20He%20has%20a%20thousand%20other%20ways%20to%20harass%2C%20as%20we%20can%20see.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPerhaps%20Rana%E2%80%99s%20past%20behaviour%20is%20colouring%20my%20judgment%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Habib%20philosophically.%20%E2%80%9CAnyway%2C%20I%20think%20that%20this%20case%20will%20be%20solved%20only%20when%20we%20know%20what%20caused%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20death.%20Ask%20Achche%20uncle%2C%20Jamal%20bhai%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuite%20unexpectedly%2C%20it%20was%20Achche%20uncle%20himself%20who%20walked%20up%20to%20them%20in%20that%20very%20moment.%20He%20had%20none%20of%20his%20usual%20cheer%2C%20and%20he%20avoided%20eye%20contact%20with%20the%20boys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAamna%20was%20trying%20her%20best%20to%20hold%20back%20tears.%20She%20sat%20alone%20in%20the%20cold%20draught%20in%20the%20veranda%2C%20refusing%20to%20look%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20Achche%20bhai%2C%20who%20stood%20by%2C%20apologetically.%20She%20saw%20her%20husband%2C%20Asghar%2C%20emerge%20in%20the%20fog%20and%20shuffle%20towards%20her%2C%20holding%20several%20polythene%20packets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20reached%20the%20veranda%2C%20looked%20at%20her%20and%20at%20Achche%20Lal%2C%20and%20began%20to%20empty%20the%20polythene%20packets%20on%20a%20wooden%20chair.%20He%20took%20out%20a%20box%20that%20said%20%E2%80%98Mother%20Dairy%20Milk%20Cake%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20then%20several%20lassi%20tetra%20packs.%20He%20gestured%20at%20them%20and%20looked%20towards%20Achche%20Lal%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20boys.%20They%20haven%E2%80%99t%20eaten%20anything%20since%20morning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAamna%20jumped%20up%2C%20%E2%80%9CMilk%20cake%3F%20Is%20this%20an%20occasion%20for%20milk%20cake%3F%20You%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20anything%20else%3F%20Could%20have%20brought%20some%20fruits!%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnly%20the%20Mother%20Dairy%20booth%20is%20open%20bhai%2C%20and%20they%20only%20had%20milk%20cake%20and%20lassi%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20helplessly.%20%E2%80%9CAchche%2C%20take%20it%20inside.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAsghar%20bhai%2C%20milk%20cake%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20interrogation%20may%20not%20be%20proper.%20ACP%20saheb%20is%20there%20%E2%80%93%20he%20would%20have%20himself%20got%20them%20lassi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAamna%20glared%20in%20the%20middle%20distance%20and%20shook%20her%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EACP%20saheb%20bent%20down%20to%20adjust%20the%20heater%2C%20then%20sat%20up%20straight%20and%20smiled%20benignly%20at%20Jamal%20and%20Habib.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20an%20informal%20chit-chat.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20take%20it%20otherwise%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20amicably.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20meet%20you%20because%20you%20are%20both%20active%20in%20a%20sensitive%20area.%20Lassi%E2%80%93%20tea%20%E2%80%93%20anything%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20Jamal%2C%20we%20have%20learnt%20from%20sources%20that%20you%20were%20instigating%20Mr%20Habib%20to%20kill%20Rahman%20ji%3F%20In%20the%20hearing%20of%20one%20and%20all%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Jamal%20and%20Habib%20looked%20astounded.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%2C%20when%3F%20I%20never%20asked%20Habibi%E2%80%A6oh%2C%20in%20his%20book%3F%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20instinctively%20slapped%20his%20forehead%20with%20his%20palm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20unruly%20ideas%20are%20first%20planted%20in%20books.%20What%20is%20this%20%3Cem%3Ebook%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20you%20are%20writing%2C%20sir%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20the%20ACP%20with%20interest.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20your%20age%2C%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20you%20first%20be%20reading%20the%20classics%3F%20These%20days%20everyone%20just%20writes%20their%20own%20book%2C%20ha!%20Why%20bother%20to%20read%20old%20masters%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20cackled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMurder%20mystery%2C%E2%80%9D%20muttered%20Habib.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMurder%20mystery%2C%E2%80%9D%20repeated%20the%20ACP.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20Mr%20Jamal%20was%20instigating%20you%20to%20%E2%80%98kill%E2%80%99%20Rahman%20ji.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20novel!%20As%20a%20joke!%E2%80%9D%20protested%20Jamal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHmm.%20And%20Mr%20Habib%20is%20even%20better.%20He%20said%20%E2%80%98No%2C%20no%20why%20to%20kill%20Rahman%3F%20Let%20us%20kill%20a%20police%20officer!%E2%80%99%20No%20doubt%20you%20will%20again%20jump%20up%20and%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98Yes%2C%20but%20in%20a%20book.%E2%80%99%20This%20is%20pure%20intimidation%20of%20law%20enforcement%20authorities.%20Such%20acts%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20%E2%80%98in%20a%20book%E2%80%99%20or%20otherwise%20%E2%80%93%20will%20now%20be%20deemed%20a%20terrorist%20offence%2C%20are%20you%20aware%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20and%20Habib%20looked%20suitably%20worried.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMr%20Habib%2C%20you%20want%20to%20become%20a%20detective%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20ACP%20changing%20tack.%20%E2%80%9CPrivate%20detective%2C%20or%20you%20want%20to%20join%20the%20police%20force%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20planning%20to%20write%20the%20civil%20services%20exams%20next%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Habib%20softly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVery%20good!%20Then%20focus%20on%20exams%2C%20become%20a%20police%20officer.%20Then%20you%E2%80%99ll%20realise%20how%20unreasonable%20your%20demands%20are%20%E2%80%93%20protest%20here%2C%20protest%20there%2C%20all%20the%20time%20disrupting%20traffic%2C%20causing%20law%20and%20order%20issues.%20Mr%20Jamal%2C%20you%20are%20to%20be%20seen%20at%20every%20anti-India%20demonstration.%20There%20is%20nothing%20good%20you%20can%20see%20in%20our%20government%3F%20So%20much%20negativity%2C%20why%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20ACP%20asked%20in%20the%20tone%20of%20an%20elderly%20relative%2C%20but%20also%20added%20sharply%2C%20%E2%80%9CWho%20sends%20you%20to%20these%20demonstrations%3F%20Who%20is%20the%20mastermind%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20cupped%20his%20face%20in%20his%20hands%20and%20sighed.%20%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20I%20need%20to%20eat%20something.%20I%20am%20not%20feeling%20well.%E2%80%9D%20The%20ACP%20smiled%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20offer%20anything.%20%E2%80%9CAnswer%20the%20question%20and%20you%20are%20free%20to%20go.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNobody%20%3Cem%3Esends%3C%2Fem%3E%20me.%20I%20care%20about%20these%20issues%20and%20I%20feel%20it%20is%20my%20duty%20to%20speak%20out.%20Constable%20Rana%20and%20Kanwal%20were%20also%20seen%20bullying%20Rahman%20miyan%20that%20night.%20In%20the%20hearing%20of%20one%20and%20all!%20Why%20are%20you%20not%20asking%20them%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20smile%20vanished.%20%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20please%20don%E2%80%99t%20tell%20me%20how%20to%20conduct%20an%20investigation.%20Second%2C%20Constable%20Rana%20was%20there%20on%20duty.%20He%20was%20surveilling%20Kanwal%2C%20and%20therefore%20we%20can%20rule%20that%20boy%20out.%20Last%20of%20all%2C%20I%20am%20surprised%20that%20your%20first%20needle%20of%20suspicion%20always%20falls%20on%20the%20police%2C%20who%20are%20there%20to%20protect%20you.%20You%20all%20never%20trust%20the%20government%20nor%20the%20police.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20trust%20the%20courts%20also.%20This%20kind%20of%20hatred%20makes%20it%20very%20easy%20for%20you%20to%20attack%20a%20policeman%20%E2%80%93%20we%20have%20been%20seeing%20that.%20Throw%20a%20stone%20at%20a%20policeman%20doing%20his%20duty%2C%20fire%20a%20katta%2C%20hmm%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ACP%20was%20interrupted%20by%20the%20sound%20of%20a%20woman%20shouting%20in%20anger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Pushpa%20Kumari%20had%20arrived%20at%20the%20police%20station%20and%20was%20making%20her%20outrage%20known.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20limit%2C%20Achche.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%20bhai%2C%20it%20is%20standard%20investigation%20procedure.%20We%20are%20only%20taking%20their%20statements.%20There%20is%20nothing%20to%20worry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20take%20statements%20from%20other%20people%3F%20Only%20Muslim%20boys%20will%20be%20called%20for%20investigation%3F%20And%20Jamal%20of%20all%20people%3F%20What%20face%20will%20I%20show%20to%20Aamna%3F%E2%80%9D%20Aamna%2C%20for%20her%20part%2C%20appeared%20quite%20placated.%20She%20came%20over%20and%20made%20to%20drag%20Pushpa%20outside.%20%E2%80%9CCome%2C%20let%20them%20do%20their%20duty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20will%20be%20asked%20for%20their%20statement.%20Why%20are%20you%20so%20suspicious%3F%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20called%20out%20to%20his%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInside%2C%20the%20ACP%20had%20stopped%20his%20questioning.%20He%20was%20trying%20to%20listen%20to%20Pushpa%2C%20his%20head%20cocked%20to%20one%20side.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20become%20an%20officer%2C%20then%20you%E2%80%99ll%20know%20how%20difficult%20it%20is%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20Habib.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20both%20free%20to%20go.%20There%20was%20no%20need%20to%20trouble%20your%20parents.%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20arrest%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20listen%2C%20deposit%20your%20phones%20outside.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20further%20investigate%20your%20networks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boys%20deposited%20their%20phones%2C%20collected%20their%20SIMs%2C%20signed%20in%20a%20register%20and%20then%20went%20out%20to%20be%20greeted%20with%20milk%20cakes%20and%20lassi.%20Even%20Jamal%2C%20who%20normally%20liked%20mithai%2C%20was%20surprised%20at%20the%20choice%20of%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ACP%20was%20slipping%20into%20an%20unpleasant%20mood.%20He%20did%20not%20approve%20of%20disorderly%20conduct%20in%20the%20station%20house%20premises%2C%20not%20from%20suspects%20and%20their%20families%20at%20any%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20reflecting%20on%20this%20when%20there%20was%20another%20sound%20from%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20had%20brought%20a%20fresh-faced%20lawyer%20to%20the%20police%20station%20who%20was%20demanding%20to%20know%20why%20his%20client%E2%80%99s%20property%20had%20been%20seized%20without%20warning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDo%20you%20know%20there%20has%20been%20a%20murder%3F%E2%80%9D%20bellowed%20the%20ACP.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20case%20material%2C%20relevant%20to%20an%20ongoing%20investigation.%20Are%20you%20here%20to%20obstruct%20my%20investigation%3F%20Get%20them%20out%20of%20here!%E2%80%9D%20he%20motioned%20towards%20Constable%20Rana%2C%20who%20was%20more%20than%20happy%20to%20oblige.%20He%20shoved%20the%20young%20lawyer%20with%20one%20hand%2C%20and%20poked%20Laadley%20with%20his%20baton%20with%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Salman%E2%80%99s%20luck%20would%20have%20it%2C%20everyone%20at%20the%20police%20station%20was%20tense%20and%20edgy%20by%20the%20time%20he%20arrived%20in%20response%20to%20the%20summons.%20Constable%20Rana%20made%20him%20sit%20down%20in%20a%20chair%2C%20grabbed%20the%20back%20of%20his%20neck%20pushing%20it%20down%2C%20and%20delivered%20three%20thumps%20on%20his%20back.%20Salman%20yelped%20in%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20did%20you%20kill%20Rahman%20ji%3F%E2%80%9D%20Rana%20asked%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20fact%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20kill%20him%2C%20saheb.%20I%20left%20in%20front%20of%20you.%20You%20saw%20me%20leave.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%20I%20was%20last%20seen%20with%20Rahman%2C%20hain%3F%20You%E2%80%99re%20the%20one%20who%20has%20been%20blabbering%20about%20my%20presence%20there%3F%E2%80%9D%20Rana%20push%20Salman%E2%80%99s%20neck%20further%20down%2C%20till%20he%20cried%20again.%20%E2%80%9CDo%20you%20know%20what%20the%20punishment%20is%20for%20accusing%20police%20officers%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EACP%20saheb%20had%20a%20mild%20headache%20by%20now.%20He%20had%20asked%20for%20coffee%20and%20two%20paracetamol%20tablets.%20He%20could%20hear%20Salman%20howling%20from%20one%20room%2C%20and%20in%20another%20part%20of%20the%20station%2C%20possibly%20outside%20his%20window%20even%2C%20some%20women%20wailing%20and%20shouting.%20He%20rubbed%20his%20eyes%20and%20got%20up%20to%20see%2C%20muttering%20to%20himself%2C%20%E2%80%9CReally%2C%20sometimes%20I%20wish%20we%20were%20not%20some%20democracy.%E2%80%9D%20A%20woman%20was%20beating%20her%20chest%20and%20claiming%20Salman%20was%20blameless%3B%20he%20had%20been%20with%20her%20all%20evening.%20Another%20older%20woman%20was%20gesticulating%20and%20cursing%20her%20for%20having%20ruined%20Salman%E2%80%99s%20life.%20A%20third%20person%2C%20a%20man%2C%20was%20pulling%20at%20the%20younger%20woman%E2%80%99s%20chadar%2C%20trying%20to%20drag%20her%20away.%20Two%20toddlers%20stood%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20this%20fight%2C%20bawling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAchche%20Lal!%E2%80%9D%20shouted%20the%20ACP.%20ASI%20Achche%20Lal%20rushed%20in%20and%20stood%20to%20attention.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20going%20on%20here%3F%20Is%20this%20a%20zoo%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20that%20one%20is%20Naseeban.%20She%20is%20publicly%20stating%20that%20Salman%20was%20with%20her%2C%20so%20naturally%20her%20husband%20is%20upset.%20He%20is%20trying%20to%20take%20her%20home.%20That%20one%20is%20Salman%E2%80%99s%20mother%20%E2%80%93%20she%20thinks%20Naseeban%20has%20entrapped%20her%20golden%20boy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20get%20everyone%20out!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Rana%20had%20beaten%20Salman%20for%20a%20good%2015%20minutes.%20His%20hands%20were%20hurting%20slightly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CACP%20saheb%20is%20saying%20to%20let%20you%20go%20today%2C%20but%20remember%20that%20soon%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to%20arrest%20you%20and%20keep%20you%20here%20for%20three%20months.%20And%20you%20will%20get%20a%20treatment%20from%20me%20every%20night.%20I%20will%20shoot%20you%20in%20the%20knee%20and%20say%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20escape.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20the%20ACP%20called%20Achche%20Lal%20into%20his%20cabin%3A%20%E2%80%9CAchche%2C%20she%20is%20your%20Mrs%20and%20everything%2C%20but%20there%20have%20to%20be%20some%20boundaries.%20I%20could%20have%20suspended%20you%20then%20and%20there!%E2%80%9D%20And%20to%20the%20others%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20police%20station%2C%20not%20a%20fish%20market.%20How%20do%20you%20allow%20people%20to%20create%20ruckus%20like%20this%3F%20From%20now%20onwards%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20any%20relatives%20or%20anyone%20else%20on%20the%20premises.%20Let%20them%20wait%20on%20the%20road%20outside.%20Sanctity%20of%20investigation%20cannot%20be%20destroyed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20policeman%20shuffled%20out%20of%20their%20superior%E2%80%99s%20room.%20%E2%80%9CYaar%2C%20who%20will%20say%20these%20people%20are%20oppressed%3F%20They%20disrupted%20every%20single%20interrogation%20today.%20Soon%20it%20will%20be%20on%20social%20media%20also%20%E2%80%93%20police%20has%20detained%20Muslim%20youth%3B%20no%20matter%20that%20they%20are%20murder%20accused%2C%E2%80%9D%20complained%20Constable%20Rana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAamna%20and%20Asghar%20felt%20hurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPushpa%20had%20insisted%20that%20Achche%20Lal%20and%20she%20visit%20them%20at%20their%20house%20that%20evening.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20was%20the%20need%20for%20it%2C%20Achche%20bhai%3F%E2%80%9D%20Aamna%20finally%20spoke%20to%20Achche%20as%20she%20poured%20him%20tea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99re%20not%20understanding.%20He%20is%20not%20an%20accused.%20We%20just%20wanted%20a%20witness%20statement%2C%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20pleaded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAchche%2C%20every%20time%20an%20incident%20happens%2C%20whatever%20it%20may%20be%2C%20why%20is%20it%20that%20only%20we%20experience%20the%20ripples%3F%20It%20seems%20to%20rupture%20our%20lives%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnyway%2C%20what%20kind%20of%20investigation%20is%20this%3F%20Are%20you%20any%20closer%20to%20discovering%20the%20truth%3F%E2%80%9D%20Asghar%20interjected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuddenly%2C%20Achche%20Lal%E2%80%99s%20mobile%20phone%20rang.%20He%20spoke%20briefly%20into%20it%20and%20then%20looked%20at%20Asghar%20triumphantly%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20police%20have%20found%20the%20stolen%20pateela!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20be%20continued%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShahrukh%20Alam%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20write%20a%20murder%20mystery%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time.%20She%20has%20written%20versions%20of%20this%20story%20since%202013%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E%C2%A0has%20published%20one%20such%20version%20earlier.%20She%20is%20hopeful%20that%20she%E2%80%99ll%20deliver%20a%20complete%20mystery%20this%20time.%20%F0%9F%A4%9E%F0%9F%8F%BB%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704637859000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F07183022%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-06-at-10.55.50-AM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-6-tetrapak-lassi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20WhoDunnIt%3A%20This%20is%20the%20sixth%20part%20of%20a%20serialised%20detective%20story%20by%20Shahrukh%20Alam.%20It%20is%20a%20work%20of%20fiction.%22%2C%22au