0the%20LAC%20which%20saw%20Chinese%20ingress%2C%20branded%20by%20him%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfriction%20issues%20which%20are%20there%E2%80%9D%20remain%20unresolved%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELt%20Gen%20Dwivedi%20said%20that%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%20are%20%E2%80%9Calso%20included%E2%80%9D%20in%20these%20two%20%E2%80%9Cfriction%20issues%20which%20are%20there%E2%80%9D%20that%20are%20balance%20because%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20are%20so%20many%20other%20issues%20which%20we%20also%20discuss%E2%80%9D.%20He%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20want%20the%20disengagement%20first%2C%20then%20we%20will%20go%20for%20de-escalation%20and%20then%20in%20the%20third%20stage%2C%20we%20will%20be%20looking%20at%20a%20normal%20management%20of%20LAC%20%E2%80%A6and%20then%20of%20course%20that%20the%20clarification%20of%20LAC%20and%20the%20demarcation.%20These%20are%20the%20various%20stages%E2%80%9D%20towards%20return%20of%20normalcy.%20He%20did%20not%20mention%20a%20return%20to%20%3Cem%3Estatus%20quo%20ante%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20the%20%3Cem%3Estatus%20quo%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20it%20existed%20before%20May%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fchina-demands-creation-of-buffer-zone-inside-india-claimed-lines-on-depsang-plains%2Fcid%2F1938629%5C%22%3EMedia%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20suggested%20that%20in%20the%20last%20few%20rounds%20of%20talks%20between%20the%20corps%20commanders%2C%20the%20Chinese%20army%20has%20demanded%20the%20creation%20of%20a%2015-20km%20buffer%20zone%20inside%20India-claimed%20lines%20on%20the%20strategic%20Depsang%20Plains%20as%20a%20precondition%20for%20disengagement%2C%20refusing%20India%E2%80%99s%20offer%20of%20a%203-4km%20no-patrolling%20zone.%20Such%20an%20arrangement%20would%20help%20Indian%20soldiers%20regain%20access%20to%20the%20five%20patrolling%20points%20%E2%80%93%20PP10%2C%20PP11%2C%20PP11A%2C%20PP12%20and%20PP13%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20area%2C%20but%20it%20would%20also%20give%20the%20PLA%20patrols%20%3Ca%20href%3D