ence%2C%20then%20what%20is%20the%20way%20out%3F%20The%20way%20out%20is%20to%20earmark%20some%20area%20which%20are%20mutually%20agreed%20no-patrolling%20zone.%20So%20that%20wherever%20they%20were%20coming%2C%20they%20will%20not%20be%20coming%3B%20where%20we%20were%20going%2C%20we%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20go%20of%20course.%20Because%20the%20aim%20is%20that%20basically%20we%20are%20looking%20at%20peace%20and%20stability.%20We%20want%20to%20prevent%20violence%2C%20so%20keeping%20these%20two%20factors%20and%20give%20negotiations%20the%20time%20%E2%80%93%20to%20gain%20time%20this%20is%20the%20only%20way%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20contended.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704637615000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F01125755%2FChina-india.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsituation-on-china-border-in-ladakh-stable-but-sensitive-not-normal-northern-army-commander%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lt%20Gen%20Upendra%20Dwivedi%20confirmed%20that%20two%20of%20the%20seven%20areas%20on%20the%20LAC%20which%20saw%20Chinese%20ingress%2C%20branded%20by%20him%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfriction%20issues%20which%20are%20there%E2%80%9D%20remain%20unresolved%20so%20far.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsituation-on-china-border-in-ladakh-stable-but-sensitive-not-normal-northern-army-commander%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Little%20Known%20About%20Mughal-Era%20'Mosque'%20in%20UP%20Where%20Muslim%20Youth%20Was%20Booked%20for%20Offering%20Azaan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F07193732%2FIMG_20240107_171246.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%2021-year-old%20Muslim%20man%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Shamli%20district%20was%20booked%20for%20offering%20azaan%20at%20a%20dilapidated%20structure%20with%20a%20contested%20character%2C%20believed%20by%20locals%20to%20date%20back%20to%20the%20Mughal%20era.%20He%20was%20arrested%2C%20and%20later%20granted%20bail%2C%20after%20being%20charged%20for%20allegedly%20creating%20enmity%20between%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20could%20not%20independently%20verify%20the%20estimated%20age%20of%20the%20structure%2C%20those%20concerned%20with%20the%20matter%20claimed%2C%20without%20any%20documentary%20evidence%2C%20that%20it%20was%20250-300%20years%20old.%20While%20local%20Muslims%20believe%20the%20structure%20was%20a%20mosque%2C%20some%20Hindus%20say%20it%20used%20to%20be%20a%20fort%20belonging%20to%20Hindu%20rulers%20before%20the%20conquest%20by%20Mughals%20and%20Afghans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUmar%20Qureshi%E2%80%99s%20act%20of%20offering%20namaz%20at%20the%20site%20allegedly%20violated%20a%20British-era%20mutual%20understanding%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20in%20the%20region%20that%20neither%20community%20would%20use%20the%20premises%20for%20religious%20purposes%20or%20alter%20its%20status%20quo%2C%20said%20Neeraj%20Kumar%2C%20the%20husband%20of%20the%20local%20%3Cem%3Epradhan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20on%20whose%20complaint%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20structure%20is%20located%20in%20Ahata%20Gos%20Garh%20(alternatively%20spelt%20Ahata%20Gausgarh)%20village%20in%20Thana%20Bhawan%20block%20of%20Shamli%20district%20in%20western%20UP.%20On%20Friday%2C%20January%205%2C%20police%20lodged%20an%20FIR%20against%20one%20Umar%20Qureshi%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Jalalabad%20town%2C%205-6%20km%20away%2C%20for%20allegedly%20offering%20namaz%20at%20the%20site%20held%20by%20him%20to%20be%20a%20Mughal-era%20mosque.%20The%20village%20Ahata%20Gos%20Garh%20has%20no%20Muslim%20residents%2C%20said%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQureshi%20was%20booked%20under%20Section%20505%20(2)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(statements%20creating%20or%20promoting%20enmity%2C%20hatred%20or%20ill%20will%20between%20classes)%20and%20Section%2067%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act.%20According%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20is%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20on%20Friday%20at%20around%202%20pm%2C%20Qureshi%20allegedly%20offered%20namaz%20at%20the%20site%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20the%20intention%20of%20spoiling%20mutual%20harmony%20in%20the%20society%E2%80%9D%20clicked%20a%20video%20and%20photos%20of%20the%20act%20and%20shared%20it%20on%20his%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%20pages.%20He%20allegedly%20made%20them%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApparently%2C%20this%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20he%20prayed%20at%20the%20site.%20A%20page%20matching%20Qureshi%E2%80%99s%20identity%20on%20Instagram%2C%20with%20over%2044%2C000%20followers%2C%20shows%20that%20his%20last%20dozen-odd%20posts%20were%20dedicated%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98mosque%E2%80%99%20and%20appealing%20to%20people%20to%20widely%20share%20information%20about%20the%20poor%20condition%20of%20the%20structure.%20A%20video%20from%20December%2029%20(also%20a%20Friday)%20uploaded%20by%20him%20on%20his%20page%20showed%20him%2C%20barefoot%2C%20offering%20the%20azan%20while%20facing%20the%20structure.%20Large%20piles%20of%20cow%20dung%20had%20been%20spread%20out%20to%20dry%20at%20the%20foot%20of%20the%20unutilised%20structure%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20compound%20facing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20written%20complaint%2C%20Kumar%20described%20the%20site%20as%20a%20200-%20to%20300-year-old%20%3Cem%3Ekhandhar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(ruins)%20of%20a%20quila%20(fort)%20near%20his%20village.%20Namaz%20had%20never%20been%20offered%20at%20the%20site%20before%20this%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Qureshi%E2%80%99s%20act%20had%20created%20outrage%20among%20the%20villagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20in%20the%20past%2C%20too%2C%20locals%20from%20neighbouring%20villages%20and%20towns%20had%20visited%20the%20site%20out%20of%20curiosity%20and%20returned%20without%20any%20controversy.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20come%20here%20to%20see%20the%20site.%20We%20have%20no%20objection%20to%20it.%20But%20in%20this%20particular%20case%2C%20those%20who%20came%20here%20raised%20unnecessary%20slogans%20and%20gave%20statements%20to%20incite%20people%20and%20offered%20namaz%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20says%20some%20locals%20refer%20to%20the%20structure%20as%20Raja%20ka%20Quila%20but%20he%20does%20not%20know%20what%20to%20call%20it%20%E2%80%93%20a%20mosque%20or%20a%20fort%20%E2%80%93%20and%20admits%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know%20for%20sure%20what%20its%20historicity%20was.%20However%2C%20what%20Kumar%20is%20certain%20about%20is%20that%20the%20structure%20must%20not%20be%20tampered%20with.%20%E2%80%9COur%20%3Cem%3Ebade%20log%3C%2Fem%3E%20(ancestors)%20had%20reached%20a%20mutual%20understanding%20that%20no%20Hindu%20would%20offer%20puja%20here%20and%20no%20Muslim%20would%20offer%20namaz%20here.%20That%E2%80%99s%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kumar%2C%20stressing%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20avoid%20a%20communal%20controversy%20over%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnees%20Ahmad%2C%20Qureshi%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20said%20his%20son%20cleaned%20parts%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98mosque%E2%80%99%20out%20of%20enthusiasm%20and%20landed%20into%20trouble%20over%20the%20azan%20as%20he%20shot%20videos%20of%20the%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20age%20of%20videos.%20So%2C%20it%20was%20widely%20circulated%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ahmad%2C%20downplaying%20the%20incident.%20He%20said%20his%20son%20was%20back%20home%20after%20being%20released%20on%20bail%20but%20rejected%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20request%20to%20speak%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnees%20said%20his%20son%20assisted%20him%20in%20his%20a%20fabric%20store%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELittle%20is%20known%20about%20the%20actual%20history%20of%20the%20site.%20The%20official%20district%20Gazetteer%20of%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20of%20which%20Shamli%20was%20a%20part%20of%20till%202012%2C%20published%20in%201980%2C%20and%20the%20much%20older%20edition%20of%201903%20authored%20by%20British%20officer%20H.R.%20Nevill%2C%20do%20refer%20to%20a%20fort%20in%20Ghausgarh%20occupied%20by%20Zabita%20Khan%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Afghan%20chieftain%20Najib-ud-Daula%2C%20dating%20back%20to%201785.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20one%20cannot%20readily%20verify%20if%20it%20was%20the%20same%20structure%20in%20question%20today%20or%20what%20stood%20before%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhanu%20Pratap%20Singh%2C%20a%20professor%20in%20civil%20engineering%20in%20SRM%20University%2C%20Ghaziabad%20and%20secretary%20of%20a%20lesser-known%20group%20Manahar%20Kheda%20Durg%20Kalyan%20Samiti%2C%20claimed%20the%20Gos%20Garh%20structure%20was%20part%20of%20a%20Hindu%20kingdom%20Manahar%20Kheda%20in%20present-day%20Jalalabad.%20It%20was%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20Mughals%20during%20the%20era%20of%20Aurangzeb%2C%20he%20claimed%2C%20adding%20that%20Gos%20Garh%20village%20was%20within%20the%20territories%20of%20Manahar%20Kheda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20further%20says%2C%20though%20without%20accessible%20documentary%20evidence%2C%20that%20during%20the%20British%20era%20a%20dispute%20arose%20between%20the%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20here%20over%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20structure%20and%20about%20offering%20prayers.%20Then%20in%201940%2C%20a%20decision%20was%20made%20at%20a%20joint%20panchayat%20that%20Hindus%20would%20not%20damage%20the%20structure%20while%20Muslims%20will%20not%20pray%20there%2C%20said%20Singh%2C%20who%20has%20visited%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20most%20of%20the%20fa%C3%A7ade%20of%20the%20structure%20still%20exists%20today%20was%20testament%20to%20the%20local%20people%20keeping%20their%20promise%20of%20not%20destroying%20it%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20said%20he%20had%20written%20to%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20on%20several%20occasions%20requesting%20them%20to%20take%20over%20the%20structure%20and%20preserve%20it%20for%20its%20historical%20value.%20He%20is%20concerned%20that%20if%20left%20to%20linger%20in%20its%20present%20state%2C%20the%20structure%20could%20become%20a%20point%20of%20a%20new%20dispute%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20can%20become%20a%20big%20issue%20in%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20the%20districts%20of%20Muzaffarnagar%20and%20Shamli%20witnessed%20large-scale%20communal%20violence%20which%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%20at%20least%2060%20persons%20and%20the%20displacement%20of%20thousands%20of%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20in%20March%2C%20the%20region%20had%20sprung%20into%20the%20news%20cycle%20after%20the%20Manahar%20Kheda%20Durg%20Kalyan%20Samiti%20submitted%20a%20petition%20to%20the%20district%20administration%20of%20Shamli%2C%20addressed%20to%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%2C%20demanding%20that%20the%20fort%20of%20Jalalabad%20be%20renamed%20as%20the%20Manahar%20Kheda%20fort%20and%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20ASI.%20The%20Samiti%20claimed%20that%20the%20Jalalabad%20Fort%20had%20been%20usurped%20by%20Jalal%20Khan%2C%20an%20Afghan%20Mughal%20commander%2C%20after%20poisoning%20a%20Rajput%20Hindu%20king%20of%20the%2017th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fort%20is%20presently%20occupied%20by%20the%20Arshad%20Ali%20Khan%2C%20the%20sitting%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20MLA%20from%20Thana%20Bhawan%2C%20and%20a%20descendant%20of%20Jalal%20Khan.%20Many%20generations%20of%20Jalal%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20descendents%20have%20lived%20there.%20Khan%20says%20he%20has%20official%20documents%20to%20prove%20their%20right%20over%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20structure%20in%20Gos%20Garh%2C%20Khan%20says%20that%20because%20the%20village%20ceased%20to%20have%20a%20Muslim%20population%2C%20over%20time%20the%20%E2%80%98mosque%E2%80%99%20turned%20desolate.%20Till%2020-25%20years%20back%2C%20people%20from%20Jalalabad%20would%20even%20go%20there%20to%20offer%20ceremonial%20namaaz%20and%20tarawi%20once%20in%20a%20while%2C%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20100%25%20a%20mosque%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Khan%2C%20though%20adding%20that%20he%20would%20provide%20the%20documentary%20references%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20detailed%20piece%20written%20last%20year%20titled%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mid-day.com%2Fnews%2Fopinion%2Farticle%2Fhindutva-eyes-a-muslim-fort-in-up-23274894%5C%22%3EHindutva%20eyes%20a%20Muslim%20fort%20in%20UP%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20senior%20journalist%20Ajaz%20Ashraf%20documented%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Jalalabad%20Fort%20amidst%20demands%20to%20rename%20it.%20Ashraf%20linked%20the%20demand%20to%20rename%20Jalalabad%20Fort%20to%20current-day%20politics%3A%20%E2%80%9CWith%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20a%20year%20away%2C%20the%20targeting%20of%20the%20Jalalabad%20fort%20is%20an%20outcome%20of%20Hindutva%20perennially%20inventing%20national%2C%20regional%20and%20micro-level%20symbols%20to%20widen%20the%20Hindu-Muslim%20chasm.%20Jalalabad%20is%20arguably%20the%20first%20instance%20of%20Hindutva%20coveting%20a%20Muslim-owned%20property.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuperintendent%20of%20Police%20Shamli%20Abhishek%20said%20that%20historically%2C%20no%20religious%20function%20was%20found%20to%20be%20been%20held%20at%20the%20decrepit%20structure%2C%20which%20may%20%E2%80%9Cpossibly%20have%20been%20a%20fort%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CClear%20instructions%20have%20been%20sent%20that%20if%20someone%20tries%20to%20start%20a%20new%20practice%20going%20against%20convention%20and%20tries%20to%20spoil%20the%20law%20and%20order%2C%20tough%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20a%20video%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20regular%20movement%20of%20the%20police%20in%20the%20village%20to%20prevent%20any%20law%20and%20order%20situation%2C%20the%20officer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SP%20also%20asked%20the%20concerned%20parties%20in%20the%20matter%20to%20approach%20the%20civil%20court%20or%20revenue%20department%20for%20any%20sort%20of%20relief%20regarding%20the%20dilapidated%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704636563000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F07193732%2FIMG_20240107_171246.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flittle-known-about-mughal-era-mosque-in-up-where-muslim-youth-was-booked-for-offering-azaan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20local%20Muslims%20believe%20the%20structure%20was%20a%20mosque%2C%20some%20Hindus%20say%20it%20used%20to%20be%20a%20fort%20belonging%20to%20Hindu%20rulers%20before%20the%20conquest%20by%20Mughals%20and%20Afghans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A49%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flittle-known-about-mughal-era-mosque-in-up-where-muslim-youth-was-booked-for-offering-azaan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Social%20Media%20Controversy%2C%20Maldives%20'Suspends'%203%20Ministers%20for%20Derogatory%20Tweets%20on%20Indian%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F07191206%2FGC_GRZkbIAAvLPY.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Maldives%20government%20has%20%E2%80%9Csuspended%E2%80%9D%20three%20deputy%20ministers%20and%20distanced%20from%20their%20social%20media%20posts%20that%20were%20derogatory%20about%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20after%20a%20social%20media%20controversy%20erupted%20over%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20Lakshadweep%20islands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Indian%20supporters%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20on%20social%20media%20had%20projected%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20Lakshadweep%20over%20the%20New%20Year%20weekend%20as%20a%20signal%20to%20Indian%20tourists%20to%20consider%20replacing%20Maldives%20with%20other%20Indian%20tourist%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20several%20members%20of%20the%20ruling%20Maldives%20government%2C%20including%20at%20least%20three%20officials%20and%20MPs%2C%20had%20posted%20riposte%20which%20criticised%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20behaviour%20of%20Indians.%20Further%20fuel%20was%20added%20to%20the%20social%20media%20uproar%20with%20Bollywood%20film%20stars%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20popular%20in%20Maldives%2C%20posting%20tweets%20that%20they%20will%20not%20visit%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20island%20nation%20due%20to%20the%20insulting%20posts%20by%20Maldivian%20ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20erupted%20on%20the%20same%20day%20that%20Maldivian%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20embarked%20on%20a%20five-day%20visit%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20afternoon%2C%20the%20Maldivian%20government%20issued%20a%20statement%20disassociating%20itself%20from%20those%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Government%20of%20Maldives%20is%20aware%20of%20derogatory%20remarks%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20against%20foreign%20leaders%20and%20high-ranking%20individuals.%20These%20opinions%20are%20personal%20and%20do%20not%20represent%20the%20views%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20Maldives%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20foreign%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20asserted%20that%20freedom%20of%20expression%20should%20be%20%E2%80%9Cexercised%20in%20a%20democratic%20and%20responsible%20manner%2C%20and%20in%20ways%20that%20do%20not%20spread%20hatred%2C%20negativity%2C%20and%20hinder%20close%20relationships%20between%20the%20Maldives%20and%20its%20international%20partners%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20also%20warned%20that%20the%20Maldives%20government%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20not%20hesitate%20to%20take%20action%20against%20those%20who%20make%20such%20derogatory%20remarks%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20hours%20later%2C%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20office%20informed%20reporters%20in%20Mal%C3%A9%20through%20WhatsApp%20that%20three%20ministers%20have%20been%20suspended.%20They%20have%20been%20identified%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmihaaru.com%2Fnews%2F129741%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20Maldivian%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20deputy%20ministers%20in%20the%20youth%20ministry%2C%20Malsha%20Sharif%2C%20Mariyum%20Shiuna%20and%20Abdulla%20Mahzoom%20Majid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20official%20statement%20from%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20office%20about%20the%20suspension%2C%20which%20stops%20them%20from%20representing%20the%20government%2C%20but%20is%20less%20than%20a%20removal%20from%20the%20cabinet.%20It%20is%20also%20not%20clear%20how%20long%20the%20%E2%80%98suspension%E2%80%99%20will%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficial%20sources%20said%20that%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commission%20also%20sought%20clarification%20from%20the%20Maldives%20government%20about%20the%20social%20media%20remarks%20of%20the%20Maldivian%20government%20officials.%20%E2%80%9COur%20High%20Commission%20in%20Maldives%20had%20strongly%20raised%20and%20expressed%20concerns%20about%C2%A0%20the%20comments%20made%20in%20regard%20to%20PM%20by%20certain%20ministers%20in%20the%20Maldives%20government%20with%20the%20Foreign%20Office%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20former%20Maldivian%20President%20Mohamed%20Nasheed%20had%20singled%20out%20Mariyum%20Shiuna%20for%20her%20%E2%80%9Cappalling%20language%E2%80%9D%20towards%20the%20%E2%80%9Cleader%20of%20a%20key%20ally%2C%20that%20is%20instrumental%20for%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20security%20and%20prosperity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20also%20urged%20President%20Muizzu%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdistance%20itself%20from%20these%20comments%20and%20give%20clear%20assurance%20to%20India%20they%20do%20not%20ref