%80%9D%20that%20efforts%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfoster%20Lakshwadeep%20island%E2%80%99s%20tourism%20sector%20has%20no%20discernible%20negative%20effect%20on%20the%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20tourism%20industry%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20such%20development%20would%20prove%20complementary%20to%20Maldivian%20tourism%2C%20creating%20opportunities%20for%20both%20regions.%20The%20synergies%20between%20the%20two%20destinations%20can%20enhance%20the%20overall%20appeal%20for%20travelers%20and%20encourage%20more%20cruise%20liners%20to%20explore%20this%20vibrant%20and%20culturally%20rich%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20association%20noted%20that%20the%20Indian%20market%20%E2%80%9Cplays%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Maldivian%20tourism%20sector%2C%20supporting%20guest%20houses%20and%20small%20to%20medium-sized%20enterprises%20(SMEs)%20that%20depend%20on%20the%20influx%20of%20Indian%20visitors%E2%80%9D.%20They%20urged%20the%20stakeholders%20to%20%E2%80%9Crecognize%20the%20interconnectedness%20of%20our%20economies%20and%20the%20shared%20benefits%20that%20come%20from%20a%20harmonious%20relationship%20between%20the%20Maldives%20and%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20official%20statement%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20over%20the%20latest%20fracas%2C%20but%20there%20has%20been%20rising%20consternation%20over%20the%20series%20of%20steps%20taken%20by%20the%20Maldives%20government%20of%20President%20Muizzu%20since%20he%20took%20over%20the%20presidency%20last%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20successfully%20won%20the%20election%20on%20an%20electoral%20platform%20targeting%20the%20previous%20government%20of%20President%20Ibrahim%20Solih%20for%20fostering%20close%20ties%20with%20India.%20He%20had%20promised%20to%20make%20India%20withdraw%20its%20personnel%20posted%20in%20Maldives%20to%20operate%20two%20helicopters%20and%20a%20Dornnier%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%2C%20therefore