uding%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fec.europa.eu%2Feurostat%2Fstatistics-explained%2Findex.php%3Foldid%3D572558%5C%22%3Eestimated%3C%2Fa%3E%20600%2C000%20fighting-age%20men%20living%20in%20the%20EU%2C%20will%20become%20a%20key%20target%20of%20Kyiv%E2%80%99s%20mobilisation%20efforts.%20Addressing%20them%20directly%20in%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.president.gov.ua%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fnovorichne-privitannya-prezidenta-ukrayini-volodimira-zelens-88037%5C%22%3Enew%20year%E2%80%99s%20speech%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Zelensky%20didn%E2%80%99t%20mince%20his%20words%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20to%20decide%20whether%20you%20are%20a%20refugee%20or%20a%20citizen.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20parallel%2C%20there%20will%20be%20further%20efforts%20to%20put%20Ukraine%E2%80%99s%20economy%20on%20a%20war%20footing%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDenys_Smyhal%2F6745%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Ukraine%E2%80%99s%20prime%20minister%2C%20Denys%20Shmyhal.%20The%20planned%20mobilisation%20will%20be%20accompanied%20by%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wilsoncenter.org%2Fblog-post%2Fukraines-budget-2024%5C%22%3Enew%20economic%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20increase%20the%20tax%20burden%20on%20individual%20citizens%20and%20small%20and%20medium-sized%20businesses%2C%20while%20social%20spending%20will%20be%20radically%20reduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeepening%20social%20divisions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20measures%20are%20undoubtedly%20necessary%20from%20a%20strategic%20perspective%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20if%20Ukraine%20wants%20to%20regain%20the%20initiative%20on%20the%20battlefield.%20But%20taken%20together%2C%20these%20actions%20by%20the%20government%20have%20revived%20potentially%20divisive%20discussions%20in%20Ukrainian%20society%20about%20social%20justice%2C%20corruption%20and%20the%20social%20contract%20between%20elites%20and%20society.%20The%20level%20of%20public%20trust%20in%20elites%20is%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkiis.com.ua%2F%3Flang%3Deng%26cat%3Dreports%26id%3D1335%26page%3D1%5C%22%3Elow%2C%20and%20decreasing%20further%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20war%20is%20increasingly%20seen%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwar%20fought%20by%20the%20poor%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20more%2C%20the%20demographic%20trends%20in%20Ukraine%E2%80%99s%20society%20further%20exacerbate%20the%20unfavourable%20long-term%20prospects%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fworld-bank-says-ukraine-has-tenfold-increase-poverty-due-war-2022-10-15%2F%5C%22%3Eever-increasing%3C%2Fa%3E%20number%20of%20people%20living%20in%20poverty.%20Life%20expectancy%20of%20men%20has%20reduced%20from%20an%20already%20low%2065%20years%20in%202021%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.elpais.com%2Finternational%2F2023-12-11%2Fukraines-demographic-drain-puts-its-post-war-recovery-at-risk.html%5C%22%3E57%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBirth%20rates%20remain%20very%20low%2C%20with%20some%20demographers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2023%2F02%2F22%2F1155943055%2Fukraine-low-birth-rate-russia-war%5C%22%3Eestimating%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20fall%20to%200.55%20babies%20per%20family%20in%202023.%20Meanwhile%2C%20emigration%20of%20the%20most%20skilled%20and%20economically%20active%20population%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unhcr.org%2Fua%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F38%2F2023%2F07%2FUNHCR-LIVES-ON-HOLD-4-INTENTIONS-AND-PERSPECTIVES-OF-REFUGEES-FROM-UKRAINE.pdf%5C%22%3Eaccelerated%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20the%20war%20began.%20This%20leaves%20predominantly%20the%20poor%20to%20do%20the%20fighting%20while%20seeing%20their%20living%20standards%20further%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForced%20mobilisation%2C%20the%20reduction%20of%20the%20rights%20and%20freedoms%20of%20the%20population%2C%20further%20economic%20disruption%20and%20social%20hardship%20contrast%20sharply%20with%20what%20is%20widely%20perceived%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Frussia-ukraine-zelenskyy-government-30e547e614babcacff2e68cecd62b551%5C%22%3Ecorruption-fuelled%20lifestyle%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20an%20entrenched%20and%20unaccountable%20elite.%20Zelensky%20himself%20may%20not%20(yet)%20be%20directly%20associated%20with%20this%20%E2%80%93%20and%20his%20relative%20lack%20of%20success%20in%20rooting%20out%20corruption%20has%20yet%20to%20significantly%20harm%20his%20own%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20several%20people%20in%20his%20inner%20circle%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fgraft-accusations-dog-top-zelenskiy-aides-2023-09-19%2F%5C%22%3Eassociated%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20corrupt%20practices.%20If%20nothing%20else%2C%20more%20fractious%20domestic%20politics%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F3ce63abc-9a71-427b-8e11-ab5309288845%5C%22%3Eincluding%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20military%20and%20political%20elites%2C%20will%20undermine%20Ukraine%E2%80%99s%20resilience%20and%20combat%20effectiveness%20from%20the%20inside%2C%20further%20playing%20into%20Russian%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20Ukraine%20needs%20a%20new%20social%20contract%20between%20elites%20and%20society%20as%20much%20as%20it%20needs%20a%20re-assessment%20of%20its%20military%20strategy.%20Yet%2C%20neither%20are%20likely.%20Zelensky%20and%20his%20foreign%20minister%2C%20Dmytro%20Kuleba%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraine-says-no-plan-b-unblocking-us-funding-2024-01-04%2F%5C%22%3Einsist%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20there%20is%20a%20path%20to%20victory%20and%20that%20they%20%E2%80%9Cdo%20not%20have%20a%20plan%20B%E2%80%9D.%20This%20uncompromising%20position%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20current%20mobilisation%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20men%2C%20however%2C%20do%20not%20constitute%20a%20strategy.%20At%20best%2C%20they%20can%20be%20part%20of%20a%20strategy.%20To%20justify%20the%20undoubted%20sacr