20the%20growing%20modernisation%20and%20increasing%20population%2C%20the%20line%20between%20civilisation%20and%20the%20wild%20has%20become%20increasingly%20blurry.%20For%20the%20most%20part%2C%20humans%20have%20been%20known%20to%20encroach%20upon%20areas%20designated%20for%20the%20wild.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20human-animal%20conflict%20has%20raised%20issues%20worldwide.%20In%20a%20country%20like%20India%2C%20which%20is%20home%20to%20some%20of%20the%20rarest%20animals%20on%20the%20planet%2C%20encompassing%20over%2024%20percent%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F130976%2Findia-forest-tree-green-cover%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20forest%20area%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20rate%20of%20wildlife%20crime%20is%20alarmingly%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20look%20back%20at%20our%20ancestors%2C%20we%20realise%20that%20perpetrating%20atrocities%20upon%20innocent%20wildlife%20has%20been%20a%20sport%20for%20humans.%20Whether%20hunting%20them%20for%20pleasure%20or%20exploiting%20their%20skin%2C%20teeth%2C%20and%20bones%20for%20our%20benefit%2C%20we%20have%20exploited%20them%20for%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Government%20implementing%20rules%20and%20laws%20to%20protect%20the%20wild%2C%20cases%20of%20wildlife%20crime%20remain%20staggeringly%20high.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2F112-tigers-deaths-from-january-to-july-this-year-says-wildlife-trust-of-india-1241859.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%202020%20alone%2C%20there%20were%20more%20than%201%2C000%20registered%20cases%20of%20wildlife%20crime.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fbangalore%2Ftamil-nadu-highest-number-wildlife-crimes-southern-states-rti-query-8846758%2